    # s "Kyou? What is he..." with dissolve
    s "¿Kyou? ¿Qué está..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:807
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_af64ad58:

    # ks "Shh, Hiroko. Just let the light take you deep once again, going back into that nice open-eyed slumber that you love so much."
    ks "Shh, Hiroko. Deja que la luz vuelva a llevarte muy profundo. Ojos abiertos mientras regresas a ese lindo sueño que tanto te encanta."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:809
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_e71d1481:

    # h sleepy "U-uhh..." with dissolve
    h sleepy "E-eeh..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:810
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_413ee177:

    # "I step closer as I see both of them seem sluggish to react to my presence, which I take as a good sign that what I'm doing is effective."
    "Doy unos pasos hacia adelante y ninguna parece tener una gran reacción ante mi presencia, lo cual tomo como una señal de que lo que estoy haciendo es efectivo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:811
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_bd88986a:

    # "Sayori seems more confused than anything, but from her rapidly flickering eyelids Hiroko is already dropping deep into trance, just like I taught her."
    "Sayori parece, más que nada, confundida; pero a juzgar por su rápido parpadeo, Hiroko ya está cayendo en un profundo trance, tal como le enseñé. "

# game/kyou 3.rpy:813
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_9ae498fe:

    # ks "Deep asleep with your eyes wide open, Hiroko. Body stiff and upright... Good girl."
    ks "Profundamente dormida con tus ojos bien abiertos, Hiroko. Cuerpo firme y erguido... Buena chica."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:815
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_a6186e85:

    # "With how many times she's been in and out of trance tonight, Hiroko's becoming very good at this." with dissolve
    "Habiendo salido y entrado al trance tantas veces esta noche, Hiroko se está volviendo muy buena en esto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:816
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_cc979b57:

    # "And it allows me to focus on the other girl, as she tries to tear herself away from her curiosity of the light to confront me."
    "Y me permite enfocarme en la otra chica, quien intenta desprenderse de su curiosidad por la luz para confrontarme."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:817
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_0f305aa6:

    # s angry_right uniform_folded "Kyou, what are you doing? Why are you even here?" with dissolve
    s angry_right uniform_folded "Kyou, ¿qué estás haciendo? ¿Por qué estás aquí?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:823
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_ecdc12f7:

    # ks smile "I'm just here to talk to you, Sayori. And you just need to listen for a while."
    ks smile "Solo estoy aquí para hablar contigo, Sayori. Solo tienes que escuchar por un rato."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:825
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_9077dabb:

    # ks "And as you listen, as you watch the light, you may find yourself becoming as sleepy as your friend, your eyelids becoming heavy."
    ks "Y al escuchar, al observar la luz, puede que te empiece a dar sueño como a tu amiga, tus párpados se ponen pesados."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:827
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_70f7bd44:

    # s frown_right "I... I am not playing this game with you, Kyou, whatever it is." with dissolve
    s frown_right "N-... No pienso jugar este juego contigo, Kyou, sea lo que sea." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:829
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_37931bd5:

    # ks neutral "You don't have to play anything, Sayori. You just need to relax. To watch. To let go."
    ks neutral "No hace falta que juegues, Sayori. Solo debes relajarte. Observar. Dejarte llevar."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:831
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_567d5e10:

    # s "I don't need to listen to this... l-let's go, Hiroko."
    s "No necesito escuchar esto... v-vámonos, Hiroko."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:833
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_c41108d2:

    # ks "You're right. There's no need to consciously listen to any of this, Sayori."
    ks "Tienes razón. No es necesario escuchar conscientemente nada de esto, Sayori."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:835
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_dea76431:

    # s neutral_right "H... Hiroko?" with dissolve
    s neutral_right "¿H... Hiroko?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:837
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_5ba76f14:

    # ks "All you need to do is relax and let the light take you deeper. Let those tired eyelids be as heavy as they feel."
    ks "Solo necesitas relajarte y dejar que la luz te lleve más profundo. Deja que esos cansados párpados se sientan y se vuelvan muy pesados."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:838
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_cb494378:

    # "As I talk I advance another half a step towards the pair, keeping my penlight passing over Sayori's eyes back and forth all the while."
    "Mientras hablo, doy otro medio paso hacia el par, sin dejar de hacer la luz pasar de un lado a otro sobre los ojos de Sayori."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:841
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_e6885175:

    # s uniform sleepy "Wh... what are you..." with dissolve
    s uniform sleepy "¿Qu... qué estás..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:843
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_f3ff2647:

    # ks "Nice and heavy. Nice and deep. And that's okay, Sayori."
    ks "Muy pesados. Muy profundo. Y eso está bien, Sayori."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:845
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_efc5196b:

    # ks "It's perfectly natural to feel like this under the light. Feeling so relaxed. Going so deep into trance for me."
    ks "Es perfectamente natural sentirte así ante la luz. Sentirte tan relajada. Cayendo en un trance muy profundo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:847
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_7af6a171:

    # ks "Perfectly natural to let yourself become hypnotized. To let those heavy, tired eyelids close for a while."
    k "Perfectamente natural ser hipnotizada. Dejar que esos pesados y cansados párpados se cierren por un ratito."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:851
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_3a92cf63:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. Deep asleep, now. Breathing in so deeply, feeling so relaxed." with dissolve
    k "Eso es, Sayori. Profundamente dormida. Inhala muy profundo, sintiéndote muy relajada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:852
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_f59063aa:

    # "I close the remaining distance between us as I hold Sayori's shoulder gently, just as I did with the other girls to keep them toppling over."
    "Cierro la distancia restante entre nosotros y sostengo el hombro de Sayori con gentileza, tal como hice con las otras chicas para evitar que cayeran."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:853
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_eeb84c5a:

    # ks "And now as you sleep, I want you to stand fully upright, and as you do so, allowing yourself to go so much deeper; feeling so much better."
    ks "Y mientras duermes, quiero que te mantengas de pie y que, al hacerlo, caigas mucho más profundo; sintiéndote cada vez mejor."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:854
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_21a85ef8:

    # "I give her a moment as I feel her no longer lean into me, then let her go."
    "Le doy un momento y siento cómo deja de apoyarse sobre mí, luego la suelto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:857
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_69f434cf:

    # "Sayori's eyes open fully, revealing a blankness that rivals Hiroko's, who has been standing obediently to attention the entire time I've focused on her friend." with dissolve
    "Los ojos de Sayori se abren, revelando un vacío que rivaliza con el de Hiroko, quien obedientemente ha estado firme de pie todo el tiempo que llevo enfocado en su amiga." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:858
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_79f937d9:

    # "Smiling, I bring my hands up to touch both Sayori and Hiroko by the shoulders. More gently this time, simply to make sure they know they're being addressed."
    "Sonriendo, levanto las manos para tomar a Sayori y a Hiroko de los hombros. Más delicadamente esta vez, solo para asegurarme de que sepan que me estoy dirigiendo a ellas."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:859
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_e24ee316:

    # ks smile "Very good, Sayori. Very good, Hiroko. Both of you staying so deep in trance for me."
    ks smile "Muy bien, Sayori. Muy bien, Hiroko. Las dos en un trance muy profundo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:864
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_9ca640fb:

    # "Anyway, that's enough musing. I need to find Sayori's phone."
    "En fin, suficiente meditación. Necesito encontrar el teléfono de Sayori."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1049
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_59024dc7:

    # "Frisking her reveals nothing, but I'm quick to find it in her bag." with dissolve
    "Palpar sus bolsillos no revela nada, pero pronto lo encuentro en su mochila." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1050
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_aba48a22:

    # k "Feeling so good, so right, so natural to stay in this blissful, relaxed trance, both of you."
    k "Se siente muy bien, muy correcto, muy natural estar en este alegre y relajante trance."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:867
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_f2a7f5a1:

    # "Sayori's eyelids flicker ever so slightly as I touch her hand, but she remains immobile while I run her fingertips over her phone's fingerprint scanner."
    "Los párpados de Sayori tiemblan muy ligeramente cuando toco su mano, pero permanece inmóvil al poner la yema de su dedo sobre el escáner de huella dactilar de su teléfono."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1053
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_d8da5dfe:

    # "It's not long before I have her phone open and my contact details entered. This is all going as smoothly as I dared hope." with dissolve
    "En poco tiempo tengo su celular abierto y mi información de contacto registrada. Todo va perfectamente como osé esperar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:869
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_1088cd5a:

    # k "And now, Sayori, as you remain so blissfully deep in this trance, you subconsciously need to listen so very carefully to what I am about to say next."
    k "Y ahora, Sayori, mientras sigues en este trance encantadoramente profundo, tu subconsciente debe escuchar con cuidado lo que estoy por decir."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:870
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_15957d4a:

    # k "You may in the future notice your phone has \"Kyou\" listed as a contact. You must immediately and automatically ignore it. It does not exist to you."
    k "En el futuro, tal vez encuentres que tu teléfono tiene a \"Kyou\" listado como contacto. Debes ignorarlo automática e inmediatamente. No existe para ti."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:871
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_bd263898:

    # k "However, whenever you receive a message from \"Kyou\", you will read every word contained within the message and then delete it immediately."
    k "Sin embargo, siempre que recibas un mensaje de \"Kyou\", leeras cada palabra contenida en el mensaje y lo eliminarás de inmediato."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:872
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_9167f120:

    # k "The instant you have done so, you will forget ever having received a message..."
    k "En el instante en el que lo hagas, olvidarás haber recibido ese mensaje..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:873
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_aeafa6d2:

    # k "... And at the first opportunity you will automatically obey the instructions the message contained."
    k "... Y a la primera oportunidad, obedecerás automáticamente las instrucciones que el mensaje contenía."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:874
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_3c1a1c29:

    # k "Then, the moment after you have obeyed, you will instantly forget ever having done so, and will continue your day as if nothing had happened."
    k "Entonces, tras haber obedecido, olvidarás instantáneamente haberlo hecho, y continuarás tu día como si nada hubiera pasado."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:875
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_6dbd900f:

    # k "Do you understand everything you were just told, Sayori?"
    k "¿Entiendes todo lo que te acabo de decir, Sayori?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:876
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_e3fb3973:

    # s entranced_talk_right "Y-yes... I understand." with dissolve
    s entranced_talk_right "S-sí... entiendo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:878
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_e057b122:

    # k "That's good, Sayori. It feels so good to listen and obey like this. Letting what I told you sink deep into your subconscious and becoming part of who you truly are." with dissolve
    k "Muy bien, Sayori. Se siente muy bien escuchar y obedecer así. Dejar que lo que dije se hunda profundamente en tu subconsciente y se vuelva parte de quien eres." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:879
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_54a9deaa:

    # k "And now, girls, you both need to listen very carefully to me."
    k "Y ahora chicas, deben escucharme cuidadosamente."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:880
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_621b1594:

    # k "Hiroko, you need to forget everything that you think happened from the moment you left the tennis court tonight, to now." with dissolve
    k "Hiroko, debes olvidar todo lo que crees que ocurrió desde el momento en que te fuiste de la cancha de tenis hasta ahora." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:881
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_98461561:

    # k "Instead, I will tell you what actually happened tonight."
    k "En vez de eso, yo te diré lo que realmente pasó esta noche."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:882
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_cf914e5c:

    # k "You finished your tennis training, then you took a long walk home. You never once saw me or Sayori during this time. That's all you need to remember."
    k "Terminaste tu entrenamiento de tenis, luego diste una larga caminata hasta tu casa. Nunca me viste a mí o a Sayori durante ese tiempo. Eso es todo lo que debes recordar."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:883
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_7c39092b:

    # k "And Sayori, you left your cram school and walked straight home. You never saw me or Hiroko." with dissolve
    k "Y Sayori, tú saliste de los cursos nocturnos y caminaste directo a casa. Nunca me viste a mí o a Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:884
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_4fa12419:

    # k "Understand, girls?"
    k "¿Comprenden, chicas?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:888
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_94eb954e:

    # multi "Yes..." with dissolve
    multi "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:891
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_b0cc8374:

    # k "Perfect. It feels so good, so right, to listen and obey. Say it with me, girls: \"Listen and obey\"." with dissolve
    k "Perfecto. Se siente muy bien, muy correcto escuchar y obedecer. Díganlo conmigo, chicas: \"Escuchar y obedecer\"." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:894
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:897
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_1546f187:

    # "I chuckle lightly. Having them repeat that back to me in unison thrills me, but that's not why I did it." with dissolve
    "Suelto una ligera carcajada. Hacerlas repetir eso me causa emoción, pero esa no es la razón por la que lo hice." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:898
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_d2ee48bf:

    # "It should hopefully cement their growing conditioning to subconsciously obey whether they realize it or not."
    "Debería cimentarles un creciente acondicionamiento a obedecer subconscientemente, se den cuenta o no."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:899
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_a88641d8:

    # k "Feeling so right... Now, when I tell you to, both of you will count slowly up in your heads, from one to ten."
    k "Se siente muy bien. Ahora, a mi señal, las dos contarán lentamente en sus cabezas del uno al diez."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:900
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_16bee9b7:

    # k "With every number, you will become more and more awake. More and more aware, more coming out of your trance."
    k "Con cada número, estarán más y más despiertas. Más y más conscientes, más cerca de salir del trance."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:901
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_c7754b6e:

    # k "And once you reach the number ten, you will fully awaken and walk straight home."
    k "Y cuando lleguen al número diez, despertarán por completo y caminarán directo a casa."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:902
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_cc32f45f:

    # k "You will not acknowledge each other or remember seeing them in any way. Understand, girls?"
    k "No notarán la presencia de la otra o recordarán haberla visto. ¿Comprenden, chicas?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:905
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_94eb954e_1:

    # multi "Yes..." with dissolve
    multi "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:908
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_e78e73c5:

    # k "Excellent. Listen and obey, girls." with dissolve
    k "Excelente. Se siente muy bien escuchar y obedecer, chicas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:911
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_640d8fcd_1:

    # multi "Listen and obey..." with dissolve
    multi "Escuchar y obedecer..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:914
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_5d443e40:

    # k "Now start counting, both of you." with dissolve
    k "Ahora empiecen a contar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:917
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_1de34f25:

    # "And with that I left the two of them alone to rouse themselves as I dashed home, feeling incredibly pleased with myself."
    "Y con eso las dejo a las dos solas y corro a casa, sintiéndome increíblemente complacido."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:918
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_a81dc9c0:

    # "I tried not to think about it at the time, but knowing what I was able to do to those two..."
    "Trataba de no pensarlo en su momento, pero sabiendo lo que fui capaz de hacerles a esas dos..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:919
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_b7b3f8ab:

    # "Man, I might not sleep well tonight, but I don't think I'll mind."
    "Cielos, tal vez no duerma bien hoy, pero no creo que me importe."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:922
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_0c51b2a3:

    # "I returned home and made some smalltalk with my dad before going to bed."
    "Regresé a casa y charlé un poco con mi padre antes de irme a la cama."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:923
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_34106a2c:

    # "The fact he's even here tells me how late it's gotten. It's been a busy night."
    "El hecho de que ya esté aquí me indica lo tarde que se es. Ha sido una noche atareada."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:924
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_052272e2:

    # "Busy. But oh so productive..."
    "Atareada. Pero muy productiva..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:964
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_793a4bed:

    # "Naturally by the next day I'm still buzzing with excitement."
    "Naturalmente, al día siguiente sigo zumbando de la emoción."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:966
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c998e9fd:

    # "When I reach the school gates, I hang around a bit before going in, hoping to catch..."
    "Cuando llego a las puertas de la escuela, merodeo un poco antes de entrar, esperando toparme con..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:970
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fbaa1989:

    # "There she is!" with dissolve
    "¡Ahí está!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:971
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2e1d403a:

    # ks smile "Nozomi, hey!"
    ks smile "¡Nozomi, hola!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:974
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_21f143fb:

    # n side sad_closed "...{w=0.8}{nw}" with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "...{w=0.8}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:977
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fee4ec1b:

    # "... She didn't acknowledge me?" with dissolve
    "... ¿Me ignoró?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:978
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b0586912:

    # "What's up with that?"
    "¿A qué viene eso?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:981
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ab0e8369:

    # "I enter class feeling more than a little confused."
    "Entro a clase sintiéndome más que confundido."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:982
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_21ab13cd:

    # "I try to attract Nozomi's attention during lessons, but every time I think I catch her gaze she simply looks away and pretends to be focused on her work."
    "Intento atraer la atención de Nozomi durante la lección, pero cada vez que creo atrapar su mirada, simplemente se voltea y finge concentrarse en su trabajo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:983
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_54d09a2d:

    # "Guess I'll have to wait until lunch with this knot in my stomach..."
    "Supongo que tendré que esperar hasta el almuerzo con este nudo en el estómago..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:992
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_70d544b4:

    # h "Well, so much for rooftop club..."
    h "Bueno, parece que no habrá club de la azotea..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:993
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b5815236:

    # s neutral_right "It's too windy out." with dissolve
    s neutral_right "Hace mucho viento afuera." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:997
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9683fe26:

    # n front teasing "At least all members are accounted for~" with dissolve
    n front teasing "Al menos todos los miembros están presentes." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:998
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_52349ebb:

    # "Nozomi and her other friends hang around in class as the lunchbell rings."
    "Nozomi y sus amigas conviven en el aula al sonar la campana del almuerzo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:999
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_27702b99:

    # "Not being able to stand it, I get up from my seat and approach them."
    "Sin poder soportarlo más, me levanto de mi asiento y me les acerco."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1002
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d1c2ca02:

    # ks concerned "Uh... Nozomi?" with dissolve
    ks concerned "Eh... ¿Nozomi?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1004
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_268406f2:

    # h frown uniform_armup "Geez, you again?" with dissolve
    h frown uniform_armup "Ay, ¿tú otra vez?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1007
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5f018811:

    # "Before I can say more, Nozomi interjects with a cold look." with dissolve
    "Antes de que pueda decir más, Nozomi se interpone con una fría mirada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1008
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a2ea9b9a:

    # n "Kyou, didn't we talk about this the other day? I'm not interested."
    n "Kyou, ¿no hablamos de esto el otro día?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1009
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a587ef7a:

    # ks surprised "The other...?! B-but, Nozo-{w=0.8}{nw}"
    ks surprised "¿El otro...? P-pero, Nozo-{w=0.8}{nw}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1185
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_61ac1483:

    # h angry "For fuck's sake Kyou, {w=0.3}{nw}" with dissolve
    h angry "Ay, puta madre, Kyou, {w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1012
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_39166ffd:

    # extend "BEAT IT!" with vpunch
    extend "¡YA BASTA!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1016
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_639d28c5:

    # "I hold my hands up and withdraw before that pink-haired brat breaks me in two." with dissolve
    "Pongo las manos en alto y me retiro antes de que la mocosa pelirrosa me parta en dos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1017
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_812f4623:

    # "... What the fuck is going on? Did I just imagine yesterday?"
    "... ¿Qué carajo está pasando? ¿Acaso imaginé todo lo de ayer?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1018
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1c0649ad:

    # "As I sit back down at my own desk and look haltingly at Nozomi's group, I notice Nozomi playing with her phone."
    "Al regresar a mi asiento y mirar con vacilación al grupo de Nozomi, noto a Nozomi jugando con su celular."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1019
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cc9aa241:

    # "She could be looking at the video we made right now, for all I know."
    "Por lo que sé, bien podría estar mirando el video que hicimos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1020
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_735c0fc1:

    # "Like she just used me and- {w=0.8}{nw}"
    "Como si solo me hubiera usado y- {w=0.8}{nw}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1022
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_289c8f4a:

    # "... My phone just buzzed. It almost never does that." with vpunch
    "... Mi teléfono acaba de vibrar. Casi nunca hace eso." with vpunch

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1025
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a1ab1978:

    # "I take it out of my pocket and find myself staring at a text."
    "Lo saco de mi bolsillo y puedo ver un texto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1026
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f5c3fc38:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"We cant talk here meet me after school again??\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"No podemos hablar aquí volvemos a vernos después de la escuela??\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1028
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_68a638da:

    # "Huh. Well, at least I'm not going mad."
    "Oh. Bueno, al menos no me estoy volviendo loco."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1029
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_16555c0a:

    # "But I'm still confused, and to be honest a little upset about this."
    "Pero sigo confundido, y para ser honesto un poco molesto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1030
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1902a9bc:

    # "I'm texting her back."
    "Le contesto el mensaje."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1033
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_15d8b2fc:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"We can't even hang out? Seriously?\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"¿Ni siquiera podemos conversar? ¿En serio?\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1035
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a88833c0:

    # "As I look back towards her, I see her chatting and smiling with the others, in-between snatching occasional glances down at her phone."
    "Miro hacia ella y la veo charlando y sonriendo con las otras entre ocasionales miradas a su teléfono."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1037
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_643de6b0:

    # "A few minutes later my own phone buzzes again." with vpunch
    "Unos cuantos minutos después, mi propio teléfono vibra de nuevo." with vpunch

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1040
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_720b2092:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Will explain later ok? Also not right after school\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"Te explicaré más tarde ¿de acuerdo? Y por cierto no justo después de la escuela\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1041
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_91474ba1:

    # "I let out a little sigh."
    "Suelto un pequeño suspiro."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1042
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fefa7b96:

    # "I never thought I'd be irritated at Nozomi of all people, but what the hell?"
    "De entre todas las personas, nunca pensé que Nozomi me irritaría, pero ¿qué diablos?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1043
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_04e7c47a:

    # "{color=#4B9374}\"Alright, come to my place when you're ready.\"{/color}"
    "{color=#4B9374}\"Está bien, ven a mi casa cuando estés lista.\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1044
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e416a620:

    # "As soon as I send it, I wonder if that was maybe a bit too forward; demanding she come straight to me instead of meeting at that café again or something."
    "En cuanto lo envío, comienzo a preguntarme si eso fue demasiado directo; demandar que venga directo a mí en lugar de volver a vernos en ese café o algo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1046
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3acacf0c:

    # "But a few minutes later I get another text back." with vpunch
    "Pero pocos minutos después, recibo otro texto en respuesta." with vpunch

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1047
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6da29739:

    # "{color=#93624B}\"Ok\"{/color}"
    "{color=#93624B}\"Ok\"{/color}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1050
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d48db519:

