    # ncg stern "Well, after having felt what it's like falling into a trance so easily I had half a mind to see if I could do it to you too?" with dissolve
    ncg stern "Bueno, después de saber lo que se siente caer en trance con tanta facilidad, ¿me preguntaba si yo podría hacértelo a ti también?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1204
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6a73c6d4:

