    # ks smile "Yeah, it's just a regular penlight that I got off the internet."
    ks smile "Sí, es una pluma linterna común y corriente que conseguí en internet."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1229
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0868c5ba:

    # ks "I took it apart, made some adjustments and put it back together."
    ks "La desmantelé, hice algunos ajustes y la reensamblé."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1230
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ab7a0965:

    # ncg "I can't even tell that it's been tampered with at all."
    ncg "Ni siquiera se nota que ha sido manipulada."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1231
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73f7b555:

    # ks "Yeah, well... I have a knack for this kind of stuff."
    ks "Sí, pues... tengo un don para esta clase de cosas."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1233
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_91e9ea11:

    # "Nozomi chuckles." with dissolve
