translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_67863b2d:

    # ncg "Oh, I was just wondering where this Kyou has been hiding for the last two and a half years."
    ncg "Oh, solo me estaba preguntando en dónde ha estado este Kyou los últimos dos años y medio."

