    # ncg "I know. It's hard to imagine you as anything but [kyou_name], but... well, that's the name that popped in my head~"
    ncg "Lo sé. Es difícil imaginarte con otro que no sea [kyou_name!t], pero... pues, es el que se me vino a la mente."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1318
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0d94e1d4:

    # "She's grinning from ear to ear as she says this."
    "Sonríe de oreja a oreja al decirlo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1546
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ad025a33:

    # ks confused "Is \"Kyou\" really that funny a name to you?"
    ks confused "¿Te parece tan gracioso el nombre \"Kyou\"?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1320
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d552b316:

    # ncg "O-of course not... [kyou_name]!"
    ncg "¡C-claro que no... [kyou_name!t]!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1322
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3d696790:

    # ncg "You just looked like a Kyou to me, heh."
    ncg "Es que te vi cara de Kyou, je."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1323
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9c0a08f6:

    # ks frown "Ugh, I do not."
    ks frown "Aj, no la tengo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1324
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9be3e98c:

    # "As Nozomi lets out another laugh, she then smirks at me."
    "Nozomi vuelve a reír y me muestra una sonrisa maliciosa."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1325
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a4c04df3:

    # ncg "But you know, [kyou_name], don't you think it's funny that you needed me to tell you what the name change was?"
    ncg "Pero ¿sabes, [kyou_name!t]?, ¿no crees que es gracioso que necesitaras que te dijera cuál era el cambio de nombre?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1326
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_38c59600:

    # ks neutral "Eh?"
    ks neutral "¿Eh?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1327
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_734c0889:

    # ncg "I mean, as a total novice I couldn't have hypnotized you, right?"
    ncg "Quiero decir, como principiante, no pude haberte hipnotizado, ¿verdad?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1328
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_abbf57b9:

    # ncg "So you didn't go into a trance and you remembered everything I said."
    ncg "Por lo que no entraste en trance y recuerdas todo lo que te dije."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1329
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6d8d5daa:

    # "... Shit, she's right. Why did I have to ask her?"
    "... Mierda, tiene razón. ¿Por qué tuve que preguntarle?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1330
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a7a6165f:

    # ks surprised "But... [kyou_name] just sounds so right in my head."
    ks surprised "Pero... [kyou_name!t] suena muy correcto en mi cabeza."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1332
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6027b9be:

    # ncg laugh "Ahahahahahahaha!" with dissolve
    ncg laugh "¡Ajajajajajajaja!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1333
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7ace5381:

    # ks frown "Oh come on, it's not that funny."
    ks frown "Oh, vamos, no es tan gracioso."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1335
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a302c47f:

    # "Nozomi has to take off her glasses to wipe her eyes as she calms herself." with dissolve
    "Nozomi tiene que quitarse las gafas para limpiarse los ojos mientras intenta calmarse." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1348
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3469d976:

    # n "Doesn't it?" with dissolve
    n "¿Verdad que sí?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1338
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d5fb5d48:

    # ks surprised "So... wow, you weren't lying yesterday."
    ks surprised "Pues... guau, ayer no mentías."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1339
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9bce48de:

    # "I can't help but laugh at the weirdness while Nozomi grins at my confusion."
    "No puedo evitar reírme de tanta rareza, mientras Nozomi sonríe ante mi confusión."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1571
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_43a318a3:

    # ncg smile2 glasses "You feel it, don't you? Like you're just rejecting your real name in your head even with the facts laid out." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 glasses "Lo estás sintiendo, ¿no? Como si estuvieras rechazando tu verdadero nombre en tu cabeza, aun con todas las pruebas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1342
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2982cd18:

    # "As I scratch my head and smile at her, she beams in satisfaction as she lifts the penlight into the air again."
    "Rasco mi cabeza y le sonrío. Su rostro se ilumina de satisfacción mientras vuelve a alzar la linterna en el aire."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1357
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d397767:

    # ncg "Now I guess I'd better be a good hypnotist and clean up after myself. Okay, Kyou?"
    ncg "Supongo que será mejor que sea una buena hipnotista y limpie mi desorden, ¿de acuerdo, Kyou?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1578
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_336be153:

    # ncg smile2 "Well, let's find out. Count to ten for me~" with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Bien, averigüémoslo. Cuéntame hasta diez." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1348
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0b87be68:

    # "I shoot her a look, then it hits me as I remember; she was trying to do what I did to her yesterday."
    "Le doy una mirada, luego el recuerdo me llega de golpe; estaba intentando hacerme lo que le hice ayer."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1349
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2d64a4ef:

    # ks neutral "Uhh, sure."
    ks neutral "Eeeh, claro."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1350
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_feec8929:

    # "But for all her enthusiasm I don't think she has the know-how to pull this off on her first try."
    "Pero, a pesar de su entusiasmo, no creo que supiera hacerlo al primer intento."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1351
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bdd30904:

    # ks "One, two, three, four, five, seven, eight, nine, ten, elev-"
    ks "Uno, dos, tres, cuatro, cinco, siete, ocho, nueve, diez, on-"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1352
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1354
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d1ed7af6:

    # ncg "Having trouble, Kyou?"
    ncg "¿Tienes problemas, Kyou?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1355
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bc11ce2a:

    # ks "No, no I got this."
    ks "No, no, ya lo tengo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1356
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_94f41c5a:

    # "With a grin, Nozomi holds out her hands in front of me, unfurling all the digits on her left hand, and just her index finger on her right."
    "Sonriente, Nozomi levanta las manos frente a mí, desplegando todos los dígitos en su mano izquierda y solo su dedo índice en la derecha."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1357
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1e030b74:

    # ncg "Sure you do, Kyou. Here, I'll make it easier for you."
    ncg "Claro que sí, Kyou. Mira, te lo pondré más fácil."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1358
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_994b607d:

    # "I stare at her fingers in front of me as I count in my head..."
    "Observo los dedos delante de mí a la vez que cuento en mi cabeza..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1373
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_37cfd885:

    # ncg smile_closed "Just tell me how many fingers I'm holding up. I'll kiss you if you get it right~" with dissolve
    ncg smile_closed "Solo dime cuántos dedos tengo levantados. Te besaré si aciertas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1592
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c0cf6a20:

    # ncg smile2 "I'm serious. So if you were just pretending to be hypnotized to spare my feelings..." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "En serio. Así que, si estás fingiendo estar hipnotizado para no herir mis sentimientos..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1595
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d1537f58:

    # ncg smile2 "Aww, so close. But I'll give you two more guesses, Kyou." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Uy, qué cerca. Pero te daré dos intentos más, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1365
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a6814ae9:

    # "F-fuck's sake! I want that kiss so I can stop pretending now."
    "¡C-carajo! Quiero ese beso. Ya puedo parar de fingir."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1366
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fe40ed4b:

    # ncg "What's the matter? You said you had this~"
    ncg "¿Qué sucede? Dijiste que lo tenías."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1368
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c0695557:

    # ncg annoyed "Really? Do you honestly think I'd accept that?" with dissolve
    ncg annoyed "¿En serio? ¿Crees honestamente que aceptaré eso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1601
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73cce5ae:

    # ncg stern2 "No. Tell me the actual number. The sum of those parts." with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "No. Dime el número. La suma de esas partes." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1371
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4884bf20:

    # ncg "For example, if you wasted two guesses and have one more, how many guesses did you have in total to get this right?"
    ncg "Por ejemplo, si gastaste dos intentos y tienes uno más, ¿cuántos intentos tenías en total?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1604
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_04aa3972:

    # ncg smile2 "Aww, what's the matter, Kyou?" with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Ooh, ¿qué sucede, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1374
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b4edf216:

    # ks "Three..."
    ks "Tres..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1376
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b9411cae:

    # ncg "That's right, very good!"
    ncg "¡Correcto, muy bien!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1377
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_846976eb:

    # "I growl as she grins playfully at me. This is a little hard to take."
    "Gruño mientras ella me da una sonrisa juguetona. Esto es muy duro."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1610
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f8ad1a7c:

    # ncg smile2 "So now, concentrate. Like you were saying, there's five..." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Y ahora, concéntrate. Como decías, tienes cinco..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1379
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8f7d63d4:

    # "But as she carries on, holding her opened hand up at me while she continues to gently mock me..."
    "Pero una vez continúa, sosteniendo gentilmente burlesca su mano abierta."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1380
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_28be23e7:

    # ncg "Plus one..."
    ncg "Más uno..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1381
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8d8cd833:

    # "And as I watch her hold up the index finger on her other hand, bringing it over to touch its counterpart, I sigh and shake my head with a chuckle."
    "Y mientras la veo levantar el dedo índice de su otra mano, poniéndolo en contacto con su contraparte, yo suspiro y sacudo la cabeza riendo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1382
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_295050fe:

    # ncg "And how many is that, Kyou?"
    ncg "¿Y eso cuánto da, Kyou?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1383
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_364eab42:

    # "I can't stay mad at this."
    "No me puedo enojar con esto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1385
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_63521ae2:

    # "She puts her hands back down on her lap and giggles."
    "Regresa sus manos a su regazo y se ríe."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1401
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0888738e:

    # ncg laugh "I believe you. If you could see the faces you were making..." with dissolve
    ncg laugh "Te creo. Si pudieras ver las caras que pones..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1387
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ea4aeb7e:

    # "We share a laugh, then after a moment she lifts the penlight into the air again."
    "Compartimos una carcajada y, tras un momento, vuelve a alzar la linterna en el aire."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1620
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_45793d74:

    # ncg smile2 "Now I guess I'd better be a good hypnotist and clean up after myself. Okay, Kyou?" with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Supongo que será mejor que sea una buena hipnotista y limpie mi desastre. ¿De acuerdo, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1390
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_926ce7e0:

    # ncg "So this is how it feels on the other side..."
    ncg "Conque así se siente del otro lado..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1613
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3c19d611:

    # "Nozomi took me back in and out of trance with a level of skill I could hardly believe, barely taking any time at all."
    "Nozomi, una vez más, me metió y me sacó del trance con un nivel de destreza que apenas pude creer, y lo hizo en un dos por tres."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1393
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9712969d:

    # "And now, having lifted her bit of trickery from my mind, I sit back and watch as Nozomi starts to gush over her accomplishment."
    "Y ahora, habiendo retirado su pequeña artimaña de mi cabeza, vuelvo a sentarme y observo a Nozomi desbordando realización."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1409
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2e71a049:

    # ncg smile_closed "The thrill of watching a subject's eyes flicker closed as they drop deep at your words..." with dissolve
    ncg smile_closed "La emoción de ver los ojos de un sujeto cerrarse al caer muy profundo ante tus palabras..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1395
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_67e28471:

    # ncg "The anticipation as you watch your suggestions take. The rush of bringing your subject out of their trance and seeing your suggestions work as intended..."
    ncg "La anticipación de ver tus sugestiones tener efecto. El impacto de sacar a tu sujeto del trance y ver tus sugestiones funcionar al pie de la letra..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1579
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8ab9efca:

    # ks confused "So... you liked what we just did?"
    ks confused "Entonces... ¿te gustó lo que acabamos de hacer?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1629
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_94ebc541:

    # ncg smile2 "Honestly Kyou, I was really just curious about doing this. Like, just to see if I could do it too?" with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Honestamente, Kyou, simplemente tenía curiosidad. Solo para ver... ¿si también podía hacerlo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1398
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_baeab484:

    # ncg laugh "But... yeah, I enjoyed that way more than I thought I would!" with dissolve
    ncg laugh "Pero... sí, ¡lo disfruté más de lo que esperaba!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1400
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9f6b19be:

    # "Reaching to her side, she picks up the penlight that she had placed next to her on the couch and grips it fondly." with dissolve
    "Moviendo la mano hacia su costado, toma la linterna que había colocado junto a ella en el sofá y la aprieta afectuosamente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1401
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0fd65ca9:

    # ncg "Thanks for giving me a chance to try it."
    ncg "Gracias por darme la oportunidad de probarlo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1402
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d199b7c6:

    # ks smile "Y-Yeah... of course."
    ks smile "S-sí... por supuesto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1403
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_71dd48ba:

    # "We share a smile, as we look to each other with a feeling of mutual satisfaction."
    "Sonreímos juntos, viéndonos el uno al otro con un sentimiento de mutua satisfacción."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1404
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0cc13136:

    # "After all this time of being ignored, I'm finally making a real connection with Nozomi."
    "Después de ser ignorado por tanto tiempo, finalmente estoy teniendo una verdadera conección con Nozomi."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1405
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c9613842:

    # "But as the moment passes an obvious question about our shared experience lingers in the air, and Nozomi is the first to give it voice."
    "Pero al pasar el momento, una obvia pregunta sobre la experiencia que compartimos permanece en el arie, y Nozomi es la primera en darle voz."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1406
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fec59e9c:

    # ncg "So... how did you like being hypnotized, Kyou? Was it as good for you as it was for me?"
    ncg "Y... ¿qué te pareció ser hipnotizado, Kyou? ¿Fue tan bueno para ti como lo fue para mí?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1407
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a83048ba:

    # ks neutral "Uh..."
    ks neutral "Eh..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1408
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3f4ec723:

    # "And man, I really need to think about that."
    "Y vaya, de verdad necesito pensarlo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1409
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d3a7c1a6:

    # "It's undeniable that she was able to bring me into trance, and maybe that alone says something."
    "Es innegable que fue capaz de inducirme al trance, y quizá eso por sí mismo diga algo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1410
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2ff58602:

    # "But now I have a moment to process it, I realize..."
    "Pero ahora que me tomo un momento para procesarlo, me doy cuenta de que..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1413
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e1c1ba27:

    # "I'll just come out and say it."
    "Voy a decirlo y ya."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1414
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6f6d2e0d:

    # ks smile "It... it was good."
    ks smile "E-... estuvo bien."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1415
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc9b1826:

    # ks "I wasn't sure how I felt at first, but once you got started and I was seeing that light? I really felt like I'd enjoy dropping into trance for you."
    ks "No estaba seguro de cómo me sentí al principio, ¿pero una vez comenzaste y estaba viendo la luz? Realmente sentí que gocé caer en trance para ti."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1416
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8f243df8:

    # ks "And knowing you loved doing this... it makes me enjoy it even more."
    ks "Y saber que te encantó hacerlo... me hace disfrutarlo incluso más."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1417
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_02e7854d:

    # "I then let a moment pass before adding with a chuckle:"
    "Dejo un momento pasar para luego añadir con una ligera risa:"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1418
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d56383a:

    # ks blush "Not to mention, uh... how could I not love waking up to a face like yours?"
    ks blush "Sin mencionar, eh... ¿cómo podría no amar despertar frente a un rostro como el tuyo?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1419
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a57b0315:

    # "I could've sworn Nozomi blushed a little as she smiles awkwardly and looks towards the floor."
    "Podría jurar que Nozomi se sonrojó un poco mientras sonríe tímidamente y mira hacia el suelo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1420
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_fe6af03d:

    # ncg "W-well... that being the case, it sounds like we could do this some more? We have time."
    ncg "P-pues... siendo ese el caso, ¿parece que podemos hacerlo un poco más? Tenemos tiempo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1452
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_addb8cae:

    # ks noblush "Yeah. Yeah, of course. Did you have something in mind?"
    ks noblush "Sí. Sí, desde luego. ¿Tenías algo en mente?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1422
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9b66ca52:

    # ncg "I... I have a few things, yeah."
    ncg "Em... tengo un par de cosas, sí."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1424
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2e96ffe3:

    # ncg "Oh, but maybe we should take turns between hypnotist and hypnotized?"
    ncg "Oh, pero ¿tal vez deberíamos tomar turnos entre hipnotista e hipnotizado?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1659
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7369de48:

    # ncg smile2 "I mean, this is YOUR penlight after all, and you did see yourself as the one doing the hypnotizing, didn't you?" with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Es decir, esta es TU linterna, después de todo, y tú pensabas ser quien llevara a cabo la hipnosis, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1426
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2791ee2c:

    # ks "I did, yeah."
    ks "Eso pretendía, sí."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1428
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_40ec6ad9:

    # ncg "So then, we take turns trying things on each other. That would be fair, right?"
    ncg "Pues bien, nos turnamos intentando cosas el uno con el otro. Eso sería justo, ¿cierto?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1436
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_76cbbf4d:

    # ks smile "Actually... maybe it wouldn't be so bad if you just did the hypnotizing from now on?"
    ks smile "En realidad... ¿puede que no sea tan malo si tú llevas a cabo la hipnosis de ahora en adelante?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1671
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e784ebcd:

    # ncg confused2 "... What?" with dissolve
    ncg confused2 "... ¿Qué?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1438
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d7863e63:

    # "Her response gives me pause, but having turned this over in my head just now, I simply smile at her."
    "Su respuesta me hace dar una pausa, pero tras haberle dado vueltas a esto en mi cabeza, simplemente le sonrío."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1439
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c6ad8a08:

    # "Maybe just coming out of hypnosis is influencing my decision a little, but still..."
    "Tal vez haber salido recién de la hipnosis está influenciando mi decisión un poco, pero, aun así."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1440
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dbb499bd:

    # "This feels like the right thing to do."
    "Siento que esto es lo correcto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1441
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e496353b:

    # ks "I mean it. Keep the penlight; I think you'll get a lot of use out of it."
    ks "Lo digo en serio. Conserva la linterna; creo que le darás muy buen uso."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1676
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d920de30:

    # ncg surprised2 "You want me to keep this? Are... are you sure?" with dissolve
    ncg surprised2 "¿Quieres que conserve esto? ¿Estás... estás seguro?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1677
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9702f6cc:

    # ncg stern2 "I-I mean, you spent a lot of time working on this, didn't you?" with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "E-es que, pasaste mucho tiempo trabajando en esto, ¿qué no?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1444
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b2771197:

    # ks "I did, yeah. But without anybody to share it with, it seems kind of pointless to hold onto it."
    ks "Así fue, sí. Pero sin nadie con quien compartirla, no tendría sentido aferrarme a ella."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1446
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1a51d315:

    # "She grips the penlight in her hands as she returns my smile." with dissolve
    "La toma en sus manos y me devuelve la sonrisa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1447
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_392d6557:

    # ks "Honestly, I'm just stoked that you're into this stuff, Nozomi. I figured you might enjoy it, but as much as this?"
    ks "Para ser honesto, me alegra mucho que te gusten estas cosas, Nozomi. Imaginé que podrías disfrutarlo, ¿pero tanto?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1448
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3b6c44e9:

    # ks "I seriously had had no idea."
    ks "De verdad no tenía idea."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1449
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ebdec140:

    # ncg "Yeah... it does feel like an odd friendship is forming, doesn't it?"
    ncg "Sí... parece el comienzo de una muy rara amistad, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1450
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c4fd3948:

    # "... I don't want to call it \"odd\" but I simply nod at her, not wanting to spoil the moment."
    "... No quiero llamarla \"rara\", pero simplemente asiento con la cabeza; tampoco quiero arruinar el momento."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1452
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a1ecc0b6:

    # "Nozomi beams as she claps her hands down on her lap excitedly."
    "El rostro de Nozomi brilla mientras da palmadas en su regazo con emoción."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1691
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_66ef0f72:

    # ncg smile2 "Maybe this is a little overambitious, but I'm feeling plucky." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Tal vez esto sea demasiado ambicioso, pero me siento confiada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1458
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_568b6528:

    # ks neutral "What? What are you thinking?"
    ks neutral "¿Qué? ¿En qué estás pensando?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1459
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7fd3f219:

    # ncg "Eheh, it's nothing terrible, Kyou. Don't worry."
    ncg "Jeje, no es nada terrible, Kyou. No te preocupes."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1460
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0b266545:

    # ks frown "But what IS it?"
    ks frown "¿Pero qué es lo que SÍ es?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1461
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8095914e:

    # "She giggles, her eyes shifting sideways for a moment before looking back to me."
    "Con una risita, sus ojos se desvían hacia un lado, para luego regresar a mí."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1463
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b94f0984:

    # "I'm about to answer as Nozomi regards me impishly."
    "Estoy por contestar mientras Nozomi me mira con picardía."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1464
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cbe332e1:

    # "... Would she really be capable of anything truly heinous? Surely not!"
    "... ¿Realmente sería ella capaz de hacer algo atroz? ¡Desde luego que no!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1465
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5612f888:

    # "And besides, even if she was, I'd simply refuse to go along with it."
    "Y además, aun si lo fuera, simplemente me reusaría."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1466
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_aed64b50:

    # ks smile "I... trust you, yeah."
    ks smile "Yo... confío en ti, sí."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1467
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d7498459:

    # "Nozomi lets out an excited squeal, then clicks the penlight back on and holds it up."
    "Nozomi suelta un chillido de emoción, luego enciende la linterna y nuevamente la levanta."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1468
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_95554b87:

    # ncg "Alright! So I'm going to put you under again, undo your last suggestion and impress on you something else."
    ncg "¡Muy bien! Pues te pondré otra vez en trance, desharé la última sugestión y pondré otra cosa."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1471
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_060a8ff9:

    # "I blink as the light hits me. A little warning first, Nozo..."
    "Parpadeo en cuanto la luz me golpea. Podrías advertirme primero, Nozo..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1472
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eae4b995:

    # ncg "I want you to start with a long, deep breath. Just like before."
    ncg "Primero que nada quiero que respires hondo. Igual que hace rato."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1473
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_519a949c:

    # ncg "That's right. Now hold it, and just concentrate your gaze upwards."
    ncg "Eso es. Ahora sostenlo, y mantén tu mirada aquí arriba."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1475
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b2df5962:

    # ncg "That's great, Kyou. It's like this is second nature for you already."
    ncg "Grandioso, Kyou. Ya es como una segunda naturaleza para ti."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1477
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0946fe17:

    # ncg "And as you watch the patterns the light leaves, I want you to exhale, nice and slow."
    ncg "Y mientras ves los patrones que deja la luz, quiero que exhales lentamente."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1479
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e93716b3:

    # ncg "Yeah. We both know how good you must be feeling right now."
    ncg "Sí. Ambos sabemos lo bien que te debes estar sintiendo ahora."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1481
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3959f1a7:

    # ncg "Taking another deep breath. Maybe not even consciously realizing you're doing it."
    ncg "Inhala profundamente otra vez. Tal vez sin siquiera estar consciente de que lo haces."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1485
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_853e6dc3:

    # ncg "And holding it, just for a little while... and release."
    ncg "Y sostenlo, solo por un momento... y suéltalo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1491
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_222433e0:

    # ncg "Yes, just like that. Maybe your eyelids are getting heavy now? I know mine were."
    ncg "Sí, justo así. ¿Tal vez tus párpados se pongan pesados? Los míos lo estaban."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1495
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_029ebe12:

    # ncg "That's what I thought. You can close them if you want to, Kyou. I won't mind."
    ncg "Eso pensé. Puedes cerrarlos si quieres, Kyou. No me molesta."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1499
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_03d981eb:

    # ncg "That's it. Letting yourself drift. Letting yourself drop..."
    ncg "Eso es. Solo déjate llevar. Déjate caer..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1502
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_73942443:

    # ncg "Letting yourself... sleep."
    ncg "Déjate ir y... duerme."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1516
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2619c695:

    # ncg "And wide awake, Kyou!"
    ncg "¡Y despierta, Kyou!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1517
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d18810f1:

    # ks surprised "H-huh?!" with vpunch
    ks surprised "¡¿Eh?!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1518
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b940b0da:

    # "I wake up with a start as I hear a loud snap in my ears."
    "Despierto con un sobresalto al escuchar un fuerte chasquido en mis oídos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1519
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_220b6ec9:

    # "Wait, where is she? I can hear her voice, but..."
    "Espera, ¿dónde está? Puedo escuchar su voz, pero..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1520
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_79608bab:

    # n "Where are you looking, Kyou? I'm over here!"
    n "¿Adónde estás mirando, Kyou? ¡Estoy por aquí!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1521
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d27a34b:

    # "My gaze snaps to look in the direction of her voice, but I don't see anything?"
    "Me doy la vuelta de pronto para mirar en la dirección de su voz, pero ¿no veo nada?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1522
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_84252fe8:

    # n "Oh my gosh, you really can't see me?"
    n "Oh, por Dios, ¿en serio no puedes verme?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1719
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2e2197ad:

    # ks surprised "Wait, is that what you did? Made yourself invisible?"
    ks surprised "Espera, ¿eso fue lo que hiciste? ¿Te hiciste invisible?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1524
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_91619228:

    # "Nozomi chuckles."
    "Nozomi se ríe."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1525
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7eaacc03:

    # n "How could I do that, Kyou? I'm no magician!"
    n "¿Cómo podría hacer eso, Kyou? ¡No soy maga!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1526
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6957356c:

    # ks "But Nozo, I really don't see you at all! How did you..."
    ks "¡Pero, Nozo, de vedad no te veo! ¿Cómo es que..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1527
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d24b4bf6:

    # "Oh man, this is freaky. I can't make out her face, or her clothes... anything."
    "Oh, cielos, esto da miedo. No puedo percibir su rostro, o su ropa... nada."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1529
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8f67d425:

    # n "Okay... NOW how many fingers am I holding up?"
    n "Muy bien... ¿AHORA cuántos tengo aquí?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1530
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9b3b6d49:

    # ks "Very funny, Nozomi..."
    ks "Muy graciosa, Nozomi..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1531
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5ae49833:

    # "Nozomi laughs, and I jump back with a start. She's right in my face!"
    "Nozomi ríe y yo salto de golpe. ¡Está justo en mi cara!"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-07-20 06:56

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1538
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_927fbeb0:

    # n "So you really can't see me? That's... that's AMAZING!"
    n "Entonces, ¿de verdad no puedes verme? Eso... ¡eso es ASOMBROSO!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1533
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_38e71f94:

    # "I'm a little pleased that she's finding this fun, but now I've had a moment to process this I can't help but feel I've been cheated."
    "Me complace un poco que le parezca divertido, pero ya que pude procesarlo por un momento, no puedo evitar sentir que esto es trampa."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1534
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8a97f24a:

    # "I did all this to see MORE of her, dammit!"
    "¡Hice todo esto para verla MÁS, maldita sea!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1535
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4f8a8134:

    # n "Oh, shoot."
    n "Oh, rayos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1732
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_61707f82:

    # ks confused "Huh? What's the matter?"
    ks confused "¿Eh? ¿Qué sucede?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1537
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_082ace24:

    # "I hear a soft sigh from my left."
    "Oigo un suave suspiro a mi izquierda."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1538
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9844e717:

    # n "I need to get back home for dinner."
    n "Necesito volver a casa para cenar."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1539
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8bfc1605:

    # ks neutral "Oh..."
    ks neutral "Oh..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1541
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_802d32f3:

    # "A moment later I hear Nozomi's soft footsteps as she seemingly walks around me and makes her way to the door."
    "Un momento después oigo los finos pasos de Nozomi aparentemente rodeándome y dirigiéndose a la puerta."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1542
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0328e2d0:

    # "As I try to follow her movements, I notice her shoes seeming to vanish into thin air as she presumably steps inside them."
    "Al intentar seguir su movimiento, noto cómo sus zapatos parecen desaparecer cuando, seguramente, se los vuelve a poner."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1543
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_53ddd225:

    # "How is my brain even doing this?"
    "¿Cómo es que mi cerebro está haciendo esto?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1544
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c1572184:

    # n "We'll talk tomorrow, Kyou!"
    n "¡Hablaremos mañana, Kyou!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1545
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2cb773dc:

    # ks surprised "Wait, hang on!"
    ks surprised "Espera, ¡aguarda!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1546
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c98c20db:

    # "The front door has its handle pulled on, then released as I call out."
    "La manija de la puerta es jalada, luego soltada en cuanto hago mi llamado."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1547
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1578a649:

    # "I mean, come on, really?"
    "Es que, vamos, ¿en serio?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1548
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4a053bfe:

    # n "Hm?"
    n "¿Mm?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1549
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bcdff63f:

    # ks "You're not gonna set me right again?"
    ks "¿No vas a componerme?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1550
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1cc92038:

    # n "S-sorry, I really need to get going. If I get home too late I'll have to explain where I've been, and... well, I really don't want to."
    n "L-lo siento, en serio tengo que irme. Si llego a casa muy tarde, tendré que explicar dónde he estado y... pues... realmente no quiero hacerlo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1551
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ec051f6e:

    # "I can hear an anxious sigh before her voice is heard again."
    "Puedo escuchar un suspiro nervioso y luego su voz vuelve a sonar."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1552
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_330435b2:

    # n "You should be okay though, right? All I did is make you think I'm invisible, that's all. It can wait until tomorrow, surely."
    n "Pero estarás bien, ¿cierto? Lo único que hice fue hacerte creer que soy invisible, eso es todo. Seguro puede esperar a mañana."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1553
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_41b09db1:

    # n "And besides, I'm sure the effect will wear off on its own anyway."
    n "Y además, de todos modos el efecto seguro se quitará solo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1554
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cb308753:

    # n "I can't imagine you'd be able to keep that kind of illusion going in your head for long. Can you?"
    n "No imagino que puedas mantener esa clase de ilusión en tu cabeza por mucho tiempo, ¿o sí?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1555
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a8542d35:

    # "I have nothing to say to that. What she's saying isn't wrong, it's just unnerving that our night is ending like this."
    "No tengo nada que decir contra eso. No se equivoca, es solo que es enervante que nuestra noche termine así."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1557
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1343c0cf:

    # "As I stand there, the door handle seems to drop of its own accord again, and this time it swings open."
    "En ese momento, la manija de la puerta parece bajar por sí sola de nuevo, y esta vez se abre."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1559
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_527d08ae:

    # n "Exactly. See you tomorrow!"
    n "Exacto. ¡Nos vemos mañana!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1561
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0b28da81:

    # "And away she goes..."
    "Y lejos se va..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1564
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_419aabef:

    # "So that was that. How do I feel about what went down?"
    "Y eso fue todo. ¿Cómo me siento con lo ocurrido?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1565
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9c192c69:

    # "I'm not entirely sure. I mean, was it really okay to give her my penlight?"
    "No estoy completamente seguro. Es decir, ¿de verdad estuvo bien darle mi linterna?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1566
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b9d08751:

    # "I worked so hard on that thing, only to let it go the moment Nozomi took an interest."
    "Trabajé muy duro en esa cosa, solo para dejarla ir en el instante en el que Nozomi mostró interés."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1568
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_89ffb3be:

    # "I did that. I made this happen."
    "Yo lo hice. Hice que esto pasara."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1570
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_22508b9f:

    # "And after tonight, I'm sure this is just the start of something wonderful for us..."
    "Y después de esta noche, estoy seguro de que esto es solo el comienzo de algo maravilloso para nosotros..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1573
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c02ab6f2:

    # ks sigh "It was a little fun, I guess, but I don't think I really enjoyed that."
    ks sigh "Fue un poco divertido, pero creo que no lo disfruté realmente."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1574
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5cb95034:

    # "Nozomi's face drops a little at my reaction."
    "El rostro de Nozomi se apaga un poco ante mi reacción."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1831
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9d139ee2:

    # ncg neutral2 "No? You seemed to be getting into it." with dissolve
    ncg neutral2 "¿No? Parecías estar pasando un buen rato." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1576
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5e25410d:

    # ks neutral "I dunno. It just feels a bit weird to be in this position."
    ks neutral "No lo sé. Es que se siente raro estar en esta posición."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1577
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1470d5c5:

    # ncg "Is that so? I wonder why that is..."
    ncg "¿Te parece? Me pregunto por qué será..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1578
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3a582454:

    # "She chuckles at she twirls the penlight around in her fingers."
    "Se ríe mientras hace girar la linterna en su mano."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1835
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ba94ce8e:

    # ncg smile2 "Maybe it's because you dislike the idea of not being in charge." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Tal vez es porque te desagrada la idea de no estar a cargo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1781
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc4b2569_1:

    # ks confused "What?"
    ks confused "¿Qué?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1581
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3fafcf86:

    # "Nozomi frowns a little as she tries to articulate what she means."
    "Nozomi frunce un poco el ceño, intentando articular lo que quiere decir."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1838
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_093b4e3c:

    # ncg stern2 "Well, I mean... we know that what we're doing is a mutual collaboration, don't we?" with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "Pues, digo... sabemos que lo que hacemos es colaboración mutua, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1583
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_83812d8f:

    # ncg "After all, nothing a hypnotist does would work without the full co-operation of their partner."
    ncg "Después de todo, nada de lo que hace un hipnotista funcionaría sin la total cooperación de su compañero."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1840
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1a44fd12:

    # ncg neutral2 "But even so, it's easy to frame it as the hypnotist being the one in control, exerting their will on their helpless subject." with dissolve
    ncg neutral2 "Pero, aun así, es fácil imaginarlo como el hipnotista siendo quien tiene el control, ejerciendo su voluntad sobre su impotente sujeto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1585
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_70630e49:

    # ncg "So if I had to guess, that's the \"position\" that feels weird to you."
    ncg "Así que, si tuviera que adivinar, esa es la \"posición\" que se siente rara para ti."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1842
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c6ff42c8:

    # ncg stern2 "Maybe you just don't like girls telling you what to do." with dissolve
    ncg stern2 "Tal vez simplemente no te gusta que las chicas te digan qué hacer." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1587
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bb1d8c7e:

    # ks "What? I..."
    ks "¿Qué? Yo..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1588
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7d57ad31:

    # "Nozomi grins as she sees me squirm in front of her."
    "Nozomi sonríe y parece retorcerse frente a mí."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1845
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d197c52b:

    # ncg smile2 "Oh, it's fine. I mean, I'm teasing a little anyway." with dissolve
    ncg smile2 "Oh, está bien. Digo, solo te estoy molestando." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1590
