# game/kyou 3.rpy:2929
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_a4f985f2:

    # s uniform alert_neutral_right "You may attempt to induce a cataleptic effect upon one of my arms." with dissolve
    s uniform alert_neutral_right "Puedes intentar inducir un efecto cataléptico en uno de mis brazos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2930
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_3390aad8:

    # s alert_sleep "It is relatively simple, and from what I gleamed from my preliminary research of hypnosis the other night, it is something of a staple at hypnosis shows." with dissolve
    s alert_sleep "Es relativamente simple, y por lo que vi en mi investigación preliminar sobre hipnosis de la otra noche, parece ser esencial en la hipnosis escénica." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2931
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d16a7128:

    # s alert_smile_right "So this would be a practical application of your skills for entertainment, in line with your original proposal, and within my comfort level." with dissolve
    s alert_smile_right "Por lo que sería una aplicación práctica de tus habilidades para el entretenimiento, igual que tu propuesta original, acomodándose a mi nivel de confort." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2932
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_3661030c:

    # "I might be a little disappointed she won't let me try something more ambitious, but I gotta appreciate her trying to compromise."
    "Tal vez me decepcione un poco que no me deje intentar algo más ambicioso, pero debo apreciar que haya buscado un compromiso."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2933
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_43f2e51f:

    # "She's still willing to let me hypnotize her, that's the main thing."
    "Aún está dispuesta a dejarme hipnotizarla; eso es lo más importante."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2934
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_31d9b77a:

    # ks smile "Alright. That's fair."
    ks smile "Muy bien. Suena perfecto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3302
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_5c7c6782:

    # s "Well, then. I do not have a lot of time before I need to head to cram school." with dissolve
    s "De acuerdo. No tengo mucho tiempo antes de irme a los cursos nocturnos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2941
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_eafdc571:

    # s "And if I am to miss my entire club time today, you had better make the best of it." with dissolve
    s "Y si he de perderme por completo el club de estudio hoy, será mejor que le saques provecho." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2944
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_accf4e6f:

    # "Taking my cue, I pull the penlight out from my pocket and switch it on."
    "Tomándolo como mi señal, saco la linterna de mi bolsillo y la enciendo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2945
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_96b17788:

    # ks smile "Okay, Sayori. Let's get to it then."
    ks smile "Muy bien, Sayori. Empecemos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2948
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_fa92a1a3:

    # "Sayori nods as she leans back on the couch and turns her eyes upward." with dissolve
    "Sayori asiente, recostándose en el sofá y alzando los ojos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2951
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_2721532b:

    # "And I respond by passing the light gently across her waiting gaze."
    "Y yo respondo pasando gentilmente la luz por su mirada."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2952
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_df3f54f5:

    # ks "Just like before, I'd like you to watch the light as I pass it back and forth here."
    ks "Igual que antes, quiero que observes la luz mientras la muevo de un lado al otro."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2954
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_18d7809c:

    # ks "Back and forth. You might already remember how this felt when we did it yesterday."
    ks "De un lado al otro. Tal vez ya estés recordando cómo se sintió cuando lo hicimos ayer."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2957
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_a2b5a982:

    # s "A-ah..." with dissolve
    s "A-ah..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2958
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_56300e67:

    # ks "It's okay. Let yourself remember as you watch the light in your eyes."
    ks "Está bien. Tan solo recuerda y observa la luz que tienes ante tus ojos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2960
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_00429300:

    # ks neutral "Focusing on those patterns as you stare. Letting yourself remember how easy it is to relax and let me do all the work here."
    ks neutral "Mírala y concéntrate en esos patrones. Recuerda lo fácil que es relajarte y dejarme hacer todo el trabajo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2964
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_02b4997d:

    # s "M... Mmmn..."
    s "M... Mmmn..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2965
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_04d062a0:

    # "I'm definitely enjoying seeing how into this she's getting."
    "Definitivamente disfruto verla así de inmersa en esto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2966
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_5bd43493:

    # ks "That's right. You can relax so fully now. Simply watching that light, allowing all the tension to drain out of your legs and arms."
    ks "Eso es. Puedes relajarte plenamente. Simplemente observa la luz, dejando que toda la tensión abandone tus brazos y piernas."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2968
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_9f39bff9:

    # ks "Watching the light as you are makes it so easy to allow everything else to drift away."
    ks "Observar la luz hace que sea muy fácil dejar que todo lo demás desaparezca."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2972
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d294856e:

    # ks "So easy to watch and drift. So easy to become so relaxed that your eyes begin to close on their own."
    ks "Es muy fácil dejarte llevar. Muy fácil relajarte tanto que tus ojos comienzan a cerrarse solos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2974
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_21c0af66:

    # ks "It'll happen naturally when your eyes close completely, and that's perfectly alright, Sayori."
    ks "De forma muy natural, tus ojos se cerrarán por completo, y eso está perfectamente bien, Sayori."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2976
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_adfa287d:

    # ks "But when they do, you'll find yourself dropping even deeper than you already are. Even deeper into relaxation."
    ks "Pero cuando se cierren, caerás más profundo de lo que estás ahora. Más profundamente relajada."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2980
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_029e18ec:

    # "Sayori's eyes gently close and I put my penlight down with a smile as I watch her. Just like I said, she's very hypnotizable."
    "Los ojos de Sayori se cierran suavemente, y yo bajo mi linterna, mirándola con una sonrisa. Como dije, es muy hipnotizable."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2980
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_f483caef:

    # ks smile "Finding yourself dropping deeper now, becoming so deeply relaxed. So deeply hypnotized now."
    ks smile "Ahora cae más profundo. Profundamente relajada. Profundamente hipnotizada."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2984
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_f02a6d04:

    # "As I look her over to make sure she's not uncomfortable slumped how she is, an idea pops into my head."
    "Al mirarla para asegurarme de que no esté incómoda ahí arrumbada, una idea se me viene a la cabeza."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2985
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_3d6e9584:

    # ks "And if you find your body is experiencing discomfort, you will be able to effortlessly adjust yourself so that you remain fully comfortable."
    ks "Y si tu cuerpo experimenta incomodidad, verás que puedes acomodarte con facilidad hasta estar completamente cómoda."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2986
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_b794dbd0:

    # ks "And in doing so, allow yourself to drop even deeper for me."
    ks "Y al hacerlo, vas a caer aún más profundo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2987
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_0ab0ea94:

    # "I watch her closely, and she does indeed shift her position on the couch; leaning her back against the cushion to reduce the tension on her spine."
    "La observo de cerca y, en efecto, cambia un poco de posición en el sofá, apoyando su espalda en el cojín para reducir la tensión sobre su columna."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2988
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_56817891:

    # ks "Very good, Sayori. Even deeper now as you feel so good about accepting my suggestions."
    ks "Muy bien, Sayori. Caes aún más profundo, y se siente muy bien aceptar mis sugestiones."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2989
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_09e1d735:

    # "So now is the moment of truth. Let's see how she takes to this."
    "Es el momento de la verdad. Veamos qué tal responde a esto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2990
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_e86dad31:

    # ks "And now that you're as deep as you are, feeling so good about being in this pleasant state of hypnosis, I want to suggest something to you."
    ks "Y ahora que estás profundamente dormida, disfrutando de este placentero estado de hipnosis, quiero sugerirte algo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2991
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_523db30b:

    # ks "But first, I'm going to need to touch your arm and your hand. That's okay, isn't it?"
    ks "Pero antes, tendré que tocar tu brazo y tu mano. ¿Te parece bien?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2993
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_5a6bc98b:

    # s "Uh-huh..." with dissolve
    s "Ajá..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2995
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_1579b05c:

    # "Even if it's what we agreed on earlier, I figured I'd better make sure she knows what I'm up to if I'm gonna be touching her." with dissolve
    "Aunque haya sido lo que acordamos hace un momento, me imaginé que sería mejor asegurarme de que sepa lo que haré si voy a tocarla." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2996
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_791aec3d:

    # "Especially as she seemed to be hung up about me touching her at all just now."
    "Sobre todo cuando parecía preocuparle tanto que la tocara hace un momento."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2998
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_34c94cf1:

    # ks neutral "Very good. So you'll notice how limp and relaxed your arm is here. Every bit as relaxed as the rest of your body."
    ks neutral "Muy bien. Ahora notarás lo flojito y relajado que está tu brazo. Tan relajado como el resto de tu cuerpo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3000
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_471e8666:

    # ks "But now I want you to imagine this arm here, and your hand, becoming rapidly stiff and rigid."
    ks "Pero ahora quiero que imagines que este brazo de aquí, y tu mano, se ponen muy tiesos y rígidos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3001
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_7e5a93b9:

    # ks "The rest of your body so loose, limp and relaxed but this arm I'm touching is becoming so very rigid and immovable now."
    ks "El resto de tu cuerpo esta flojito y relajado, pero este brazo que estoy tocando ahora está muy rígido e inmóvil."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3003
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_7d140fcd:

    # ks smile "Very good, Sayori. That arm is now locked into place as it is."
    ks smile "Muy bien, Sayori. Este brazo ahora está bloqueado en esa posición."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3005
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_822a67c7:

    # ks "You might try to move this hand and this arm at any time, but the more you try, the more stiff and rigid it becomes."
    ks "Puedes intentar mover esta mano y este brazo cuando quieras, pero entre más lo intentas, más tiesos y rígidos se ponen."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3006
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_535af29b:

    # ks "The more you try, the more immovable it gets... And in just a few moments I'm going to return you to a state of waking, Sayori."
    ks "Entre más lo intentas, más inmóvil se vuelve... Y en unos momentos voy a despertarte otra vez, Sayori."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3007
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_95b200c2:

    # ks "I'm going to count, and you're going to awaken on five."
    ks "Voy a contar y tú despertarás cuando llegue a cinco."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3009
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_7d3a9412:

    # ks "Starting to count up now... one, two, three..."
    ks "Contaré ahora... uno, dos, tres..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3014
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_ef33fd4b:

    # s "Uurrhm..."
    s "Aamnn..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3015
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_919970e0:

    # "Her lethargic moan gets a chuckle out of me as her eyelids swivel open and she looks up at me."
    "Su quejido letárgico me hace reír un poco. Sus ojos se abren para mirarme."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3016
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_94a59410:

    # ks "How are you feeling?"
    ks "¿Cómo te sientes?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3017
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_aee042db:

    # "She begins to answer me, but her reply dies on her lips as she comes to a sudden realization."
    "Comienza a intentar contestarme, pero su respuesta perece en sus labios al darse cuenta repentinamente de lo que está pasando."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3020
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_0c73b073:

    # s "Ahh!" with dissolve
    s "¡Aah!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3022
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_2a1d1d84:

    # s "Kyou, I... I am not sure how to feel about this."
    s "Kyou, N-... no estoy segura de cómo sentirme ante esto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3023
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_573a86e9:

    # "I look at Sayori's immobilized arm, then back at her."
    "Miro el brazo inmovilizado de Sayori, luego a ella otra vez."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3024
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_e5861e68:

    # ks neutral "What's wrong?"
    ks neutral "¿Cuál es el problema?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3026
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_b75a815a:

    # "She frowns as her body tenses." with dissolve
    "Frunce el ceño y su cuerpo se tensa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3027
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_421d25ed:

    # s "Mmpth... You did this?!"
    s "Mm... ¡¿Tú hiciste esto?!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3028
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_510abd24:

    # "I flash her a triumphant smirk."
    "Le muestro una sonrisa triunfante."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3029
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_01d58ac9:

    # ks smirk "Who else would it be?"
    ks smirk "¿Y quién más?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3030
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_bad21a62:

    # "Sayori scoffs as she turns her attention back to her arm, bringing her right hand over to tentatively tug at its sleeve."
    "Sayori se mofa y devuelve su atención a su brazo, acercando su mano derecha para tirar cuidadosamente de su manga."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3031
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_83d8d43e:

    # ks smile "So... I wanna ask again how you're feeling."
    ks smile "Y... Quisiera preguntar de nuevo: ¿cómo te sientes?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3033
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_7d705efb:

    # s "Hmm..." with dissolve
    s "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3036
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_871ec494:

    # "She doesn't tug particularly hard, maybe worried she'll injure herself, and returns her free hand to the couch as she purses her lips in thought."
    "No jala particularmente fuerte, tal vez preocupada por lastimarse; luego devuelve su mano libre a su regazo y frunce sus labios pensando."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3035
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d75ad968:

    # s "I truly feel like my arm is no longer my own. I can barely even detect any sensations from it."
    s "Realmente siento que mi brazo ya no me pertenece. Apenas puedo percibir sensaciones con él."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3042
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_65aeefcb:

    # "Sayori sucks in a breath through her nose, then almost immediately sighs the air back out in defeat."
    "Sayori toma aire por la nariz, luego casi inmediatamente vuelve a expulsar el aire con resignación."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3040
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_700f7d19:

    # s "If you can perform this at the culture festival, you have the makings of a good show."
    s "Si puedes llevar esto acabo en el festival cultural, con seguridad darás un buen espectáculo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3041
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d8a268c8:

    # s "And once again Kyou, I am fascinated and disturbed by what you are capable of."
    s "Y, una vez más, Kyou, estoy fascinada y perturbada al ver de lo que eres capaz."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3042
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_0da34816:

    # "I chuckle nervously in response, but I have to ask."
    "Me río nerviosamente en respuesta, pero debo preguntar."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3043
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_b0c73b23:

    # ks neutral "Is this stuff really that disturbing to you?"
    ks neutral "¿Todo esto de verdad te parece tan perturbador?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3045
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_a9509e3b:

    # "She looks uncomfortably away from me, as her arm remains tethered to the air." with dissolve
    "Me aparta la mirada incómodamente, con su brazo aún atado al aire." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3047
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_ec226f9d:

    # s "It is as I said. It bothers me that you appear to have such a level of control over me that I cannot explain." with dissolve
    s "Como dije antes: Me molesta que parezcas tener este nivel de control sobre mí el cual no puedo explicar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3050
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_f8648a29:

    # s "But truly, to me your ability to influence me feels... total." with dissolve
    s "Pero, de verdad, tu habilidad para influenciarme se siente... absoluta." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3051
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_b6dcfd83:

    # "She's still having trouble believing she's truly okay with being hypnotized and accepting my suggestions."
    "Aún le cuesta creer que realmente no tiene problemas en dejarme hipnotizarla y aceptar mis sugestiones."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3052
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_cee2d8b1:

    # "I'm kinda tempted to poke fun at her for thinking I'm mind-controlling her or something, but... no."
    "Estoy tentado a burlarme de ella por creer que estoy controlando su mente o algo, pero... no."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3057
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d5098301:

    # "Sayori's just really good at being hypnotized, and I'm sure on some level she's enjoying this as much as I am."
    "Sayori simplemente es muy buena siendo hipnotizada, y estoy seguro de que, en cierto nivel, disfruta esto tanto como yo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3054
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_2451c7a4:

    # "I want to encourage her."
    "Quiero motivarla."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3056
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_c591e642:

    # ks smile "Hey, maybe you'll feel better about it after a few more sessions." with dissolve
    ks smile "Bueno, tal vez te sientas mejor al respecto luego de unas cuantas sesiones más." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3057
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_2dd778fe:

    # ks "It might seem weird to start, but I'm sure you'll feel more confident about it soon."
    ks "Puede parecer extraño al principio, pero estoy seguro de que pronto sentirás más confianza."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3058
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_5770de16:

    # ks "Maybe you could study hypnosis yourself a little more if that'll put your mind at ease?"
    ks "Tal vez puedas estudiar hipnosis un poco más por ti misma si es que eso te tranquiliza."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3060
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d937ece3:

    # "Sayori lets off a chuckle of her own this time." with dissolve
    "Ahora es Sayori quien suelta una risita." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3065
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_f67c82e0:

    # s "My... It sounds like you are giving me homework."
    s "Vaya... Suena a que me estás dando tarea."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3071
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_b42af510:

    # s "But for now, I need to be going and it seems I need your assistance."
    s "Pero, por ahora, me tengo que ir, y parece que preciso tu asistencia."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3067
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d65ef996:

    # "I smile and nod at her, and just then I realize I can impart a little wisdom upon her."
    "Le sonrío y asiento con la cabeza, y entonces me doy cuenta de que puedo impartirle un poco de sabiduría."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3068
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_08dcee39:

    # ks "Alright. And while I'm at it, there's something else I can teach you about hypnosis."
    ks "Muy bien. Y ya que estoy en eso, hay algo más que puedo enseñarte sobre hipnossi."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3070
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_4f3c6c90:

    # s "Is that so?" with dissolve
    s "¿En serio?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3071
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_d958baa2:

    # ks "Yeah. So maybe you learned about this already, but you know you've been in a light state of hypnotic trance this whole time we've been talking, right?"
    ks "Sí. Tal vez ya aprendiste sobre esto, pero sabes que has estado en un ligero estado de trance hipnótico durante toda nuestra charla, ¿verdad?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3073
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_fdaafa50:

    # s "Wh- what?! Is that true?" with dissolve
    s "¡¿Qu- qué?! ¿Es eso cierto?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3074
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_03236fd9:

    # "Oh man, she really is surprised. And I gotta admit, it's a little boost to my ego to know something she doesn't."
    "Oh, cielos, está muy sorprendida. Debo admitir que es un regalo para mi ego saber algo que ella no."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3075
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_2d831efa:

    # ks "Yeah. The fact that you're still under hypnotic suggestion-"
    ks "Sí. El hecho de que sigas bajo una sugestión hipnótica-"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3077
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_b4dd5648:

    # ks "- means you're in this kind of half trance. And because of that, I think you'll find it very easy to drop fully back into trance at my suggestion."
