translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_659ef18f:

    # "Anyway, I carefully take a seat beside her and gently close my fingers around her left wrist."
    "Como sea, cuidadosamente me siento junto a ella y, con gentileza, tomo su muñeca izquierda entre mis dedos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2988
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_f6640c39:

    # "As I speak I begin to lift her arm off the couch, keeping it held in the air as I continue."
    "Mientras hablo, comienzo a levantar su brazo del sofá y, sosteniéndolo en el aire, continúo."

