    # "I smile as I feel her arm begin to tighten up as I'm holding it."
    "Sonrío al sentir que su brazo comienza a tensarse mientras lo sujeto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2993
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_da0c4d27:

    # "I then stroke the back of her outstretched wrist a little as I continue to solidify the suggestion in her subconscious."
    "Luego sacudo levemente el dorso de su mano y continúo solidificando la sugestión en su subconsciente."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2995
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_78071cb9:

    # ks "The more you try, the more immovable it gets... Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "Entre más lo intentes, más se inmoviliza... ¿Comprendes?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2998
translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_1aa3577b:

    # s "Uh-huh... I understand."
    s "Ajá... Comprendo."

