translate spanish Day3_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Switch_de64b85b:

    # "As I slowly pull my hand back, I nod with satisfaction at how her arm remains suspended in front of me."
    "Retiro lentamente mi mano, asintiendo con satisfacción al ver que su brazo permanece suspendido ante mí."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:3002
