    "Con un suspiro, trato de mantener la cabeza fría y pensarlo con cuidado."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:522
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_5e5e0ae6:

    # ks "Alright, Hiroko. You've made your point."
    ks "Está bien, Hiroko. Ya aclaraste tu punto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:523
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_b40ba08e:

    # "After all, what's important here is how much she's already adapted to life as my [hypno6]."
    "Después de todo, lo importante aquí es lo bien que se ha adaptado a su vida como mi [hypno6!t!l]."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:524
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_21ab9546:

    # h neutral "So you're gonna do it?" with dissolve
    h neutral "¿O sea que vas a hacerlo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:525
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_877ae98d:

    # "She's retained all of yesterday's programming and she doesn't seem to be fighting it at all."
    "Aún retiene toda la programación de ayer y no parece oponerse a ella en lo más mínimo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:536
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_489b092f:

    # h nervous "Kyou?" with dissolve
    h nervous "¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:527
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_60986ae4:

    # "Not to mention, I could even use her own passions to enhance her robotic conditioning even further."
    "Sin mencionar que tal vez incluso pueda usar sus propias pasiones para intensificar su acondicionamiento robótico todavía más."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:528
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_550107d1:

    # "So why get upset? Indulging her could be interesting."
    "Así que, ¿para qué enfadarme? Darle lo que quiere podría ser interesante."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:529
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_a34e6aa6:

    # ks frown "I'll consider it. Although I do have to wonder..."
    ks frown "Lo consideraré. Sin embargo, me pregunto..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:530
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_beeeb5d4:

    # h frown "Wonder what?" with dissolve
    h frown "¿Qué te preguntas?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:531
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_27eba4f6:

    # ks smirk "Wonder whether it's legal for a [hypno6] to compete with humans in a professional sport."
    ks smirk "Me pregunto si será legal que un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] compita con humanas en un deporte profesional."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:532
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_38fafce8:

    # h tennis_armup surprised "Ahh!" with dissolve
    h tennis_armup surprised "¡Aah!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:533
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_20714453:

    # "Raising the issue makes her visibly cringe. Guess she hadn't considered that in all her excitement."
    "Plantear la cuestión la pone a temblar. Supongo que no lo había considerado entre tanta emoción."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:547
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_d3ea6bbf:

    # h tennis_headhold2 sad_side "S-shit, you're right. The first time I gotta do a blood test I'm gonna be found out." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 sad_side "M-mierta, es cierto. A la primera que me toque hacer un examen de sangre me descubrirán." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:548
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_71436914:

    # h sleeptalk_concerned "Ain't no two ways about it." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk_concerned "Ya valió." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:540
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_5f3c48d6:

    # ks smile "Actually, that's not going to be an issue for you."
    ks smile "En realidad eso no será un problema para ti."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:554
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_a3b23ed0:

    # h tennis surprised "Huh? Whaddya mean?" with dissolve
    h tennis surprised "¿Eh? ¿A qué te refieres?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:542
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_7c56f38b:

    # ks "It's like I told you: You were built in an advanced facility with the aim of having you live among humans."
    ks "Como dije: fuiste fabricada en un centro avanzado con el objetivo de vivir entre los humanos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:544
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_12073778:

    # ks "Your body mimics normal human functions. If it didn't you would've been discovered years ago." with dissolve
    ks "Tu cuerpo simula funciones humanas normales. De no ser así, ya te habrían descubierto hace años." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:545
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_5285cc10:

    # ks "So don't worry. You can \"bleed\" in all the places a regular human does, and no one will be able to tell the difference."
    ks "Así que no te preocupes. Puedes \"sangrar\" por los mismos lugares que un humano común y corriente, y nadie notará la diferencia."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:559
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_bc73257a:

    # h tennis_armup shocked "Shit, for real?!" with dissolve
    h tennis_armup shocked "Mierda, ¡¿de veras?!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:547
translate spanish Day3_Villain_Kyou_c33d2ba1:

