# game/kyou 3.rpy:2273
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_8b2d0853:

    # "But as I go to her and see her face again, I can only believe she isn't listening to anything I have to say."
    "Pero al caminar hacia ella y volver a ver su cara, es evidente que no escucha nada de lo que digo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2276
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_2a01b4ad:

    # "Because right now she's only interested in one thing."
    "Porque ahora mismo solo le interesa una cosa."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2278
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_c59ef042:

    # n "Brraaaaaiiiiiin!"
    n "¡Cereeeeeeebroooo!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2286
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_365bfa4e:

    # "And a slow pounding on my bedroom door confirms Nozomi has no intention of stopping." with vpunch
    "Y un lento golpeteo en la puerta de mi habitación confirma que Nozomi no tiene intenciones de parar." with vpunch

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2296
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_0910e22c:

    # ks smile "If ever we are no longer alone or in this house, the phrase \"[hypno3]\" and its effects will not influence you in any way."
    ks smile "Si en algún momento ya no estamos solos o en esta casa, la palabra \"[hypno3!t!l]\" y sus efectos dejarán de influenciarte de cualquier manera."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2321
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_164d914a:

    # "She just missed biting into my head, but she got a good chunk of my hair with those chompers of hers."
    "Por poco me muerde la cabeza, pero sí me arrancó gran mechón de cabello con esas fauces."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2339
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_e10dcf92:

    # "An instant later, Nozomi moves her hands from out in front of her to tightly clutch her head as she starts to cry out in pain." with dissolve
    "Un instante después, las manos de Nozomi pasan de estar delante de ella a sujetar firmemente su cabeza, y ella empieza a llorar de dolor." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2381
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_1d1556ab:

    # n determined "I SAID I can handle it." with dissolve
    n determined "DIJE que puedo con esto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:2390
translate spanish Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Day3_HypnoSesh_784ee5c7:

