# game/kyou 3.rpy:1142
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_cd80a307:

    # "I bring my anxieties with me to the next morning on my way to school."
    "Traigo mis ansiedades conmigo a la mañana siguiente camino a la escuela."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1148
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_c6a07cca:

    # "As I roll up to the school gates, I catch the sight of Hiroko as she crosses my path on the way in."
    "Mientras me aproximo a las puertas de la escuela, veo a Hiroko cruzar mi camino."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1149
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_42b43932:

    # h frown "..." with dissolve
    h frown "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1150
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_4cc5387a:

    # h angry "Piece of shit." with dissolve
    h angry "Pedazo de mierda." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1152
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_0794166e:

    # "Yeah, she saw me too. At least she's predictable." with dissolve
    "Sí, ella también me vio. Al menos es predecible." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1154
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_276fe105:

    # "I let Hiroko walk in ahead before taking my seat ready to get the day started."
    "Dejo que Hiroko entre primero, para luego tomar asiento y comenzar el día."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1155
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_fa1d339c:

    # a "Is Koyama here yet?"
    a "¿Se encuentra Koyama?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1156
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_5c4c3ea3:

    # "Although practically the moment I get settled, I hear a familiar voice and as I look across to the door my eyes meet those of our student council president."
    "Aunque prácticamente el instante en que me siento, oigo una voz familiar, y al voltear a la puerta, mi mirada se cruza con la de la presidenta del consejo estudiantil."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1157
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_e3d712a7:

    # a "Ah good, there you are."
    a "Ah, qué bien, ahí estás."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1159
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_28e9b79e:

    # "My classmates start looking my way as Akiko walks over to me, an uncomfortable expression on her face." with dissolve
    "Mis compañeros comienzan a mirarme mientras Akiko camina hacia mí con una incómoda expresión en su rostro." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1160
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_3b0b328e:

    # ks confused "Good... morning?"
    ks confused "¿Buenos... días?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1161
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_e733b63b:

    # "This certainly isn't doing my anxiety any favors. This doesn't look good to me at all."
    "Esto ciertamente no ayuda con mi ansiedad. No luce nada bien para mí."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1162
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_b5a83f3d:

    # a uniform_down armband_down "Good morning, Koyama. Please join me for lunch later on. We'll use the student council room." with dissolve
    a uniform_down armband_down "Buenos días, Koyama. Por favor, acompáñame durante el almuerzo más tarde. Usaremos la sala del consejo estudiantil." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1163
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_cf17326e:

    # ks "Uh, okay... why?"
    ks "Eh, está bien... ¿por qué?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1164
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_d1d41028:

    # a frown_side "It's... it's just important, okay? It concerns your behaviour yesterday." with dissolve
    a frown_side "Es... es importante, ¿de acuerdo? Concierne tu comportamiento de ayer." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1165
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_728d4e0b:

    # h "Oh yeah? Why don'tcha tell Kobayashi about it, 'Kiko?"
    h "¿Ah, sí? ¿Y por qué no le dices a Kobayashi, 'Kiko?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1170
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_9fbc62c8:

    # "Great. My day's just getting started and it looks like everyone's already set for round two of \"Girls shitting on Kyou for no good reason\"." with dissolve
    "Genial. Mi día acaba de empezar, y ya parece que todos están listos para la segunda ronda de \"Chicas lanzándole mierda a Kyou sin una buena razón\"." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1172
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_31fa31d2:

    # s uniform_handup neutral "I do not understand this approach you are taking, Akiko. What business is it of yours to take such a personal involvement in our situation?" with dissolve
    s uniform_handup neutral "No comprendo tu acercamiento, Akiko. ¿De qué modo te concierne nuestra situación como para involucrarte de forma tan personal?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1173
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_82f7fd9d:

    # s frown "If you are sincere in your interest then it would surely be a better use of your time to present your concerns to Kobayashi with the rest of us." with dissolve
    s frown "Si tu interés es sincero, ciertamente sería mejor presentarle tus inquietudes a Kobayashi junto al resto de nosotras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1174
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_685592fa:

    # s "Were you to add your voice to ours, he may actually take us seriously this time."
    s "Si adicionas tu voz a la nuestra, puede que nos tomen en serio esta vez."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1175
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_629e3874:

    # "They could at least not do it by my desk..."
    "Al menos podrían no hacer esto junto a mi escritorio..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1176
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_883448d0:

    # a uniform armband sigh "Ahh, no, I really don't think we need to take it that far, you guys." with dissolve
    a uniform armband sigh "Aah, no, realmente no creo que sea necesario llevarlo tan lejos, chicas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1177
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_a7ab3d4f:

    # h uniform_armup irritated vein "For {nw}" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup irritated vein "¡La {nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1178
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_b2b44b8c:

    # extend "FUCK'S sake, lady! What've we gotta do to make you do your job around here?" with vpunch
    extend "PUTA madre, señorita! ¿Qué hay que hacer para que te pongas a hacer tu trabajo por aquí?" with vpunch

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1179
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_cf0a364d:

    # a frown_side "What do you think my job even is, Homura?" with dissolve
    a frown_side "¿Y cuál crees tú que es mi trabajo, Homura?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1181
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_592b7ae7:

    # s uniform_folded irritated "I shall give you a hint, Hiroko. Her job does not involve practicing her brand of amateur psychology to a captive audience." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded irritated "Te daré una pista, Hiroko. No involucra practicar su psicología amateur ante una audiencia cautiva." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1182
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_58f9476b:

    # a sigh "Ugh, don't you start too, Sayori. I just think this situation needs an outside perspective from a fellow student, that's all." with dissolve
    a sigh "Ay, no empieces tú también, Sayori. Solo creo que esta situación requiere una perspectiva externa de un estudiante, es todo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1185
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_53d847ea:

    # a sad_side "If nothing comes of it I'll talk to Kobayashi myself, okay?" with dissolve
    a sad_side "Si no llegamos a nada, hablaré con Kobayashi yo misma, ¿de acuerdo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1186
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_8c8b447c:

    # s uniform_handup "Do as you like. But if he approaches Nozomi again you may both come to regret it." with dissolve
    s uniform_handup "Haz lo que plazca. Pero si vuelve a acercarse a Nozomi, puede que los dos se arrepientan." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1189
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_1e77c4b4:

    # "And with that parting shot, the two girls stomp back to their desks." with dissolve
    "Y con ese disparo de despedida, las dos chicas regresan marchando a sus escritorios." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1191
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_df884f24:

    # "At least Nozomi wasn't around for any of that..." with dissolve
    "Al menos Nozomi no estaba mientras esto ocurría..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1192
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_6dc5bfeb:

    # a sigh "{size=16}Ugh, what am I even doing here?{/size}" with dissolve
    a sigh "{size=16}Ay, pero ¿qué estoy haciendo aquí?{/size}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1193
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f673566d:

    # "Where is she anyway? It's almost time for homeroom to start."
    "¿Y dónde está, a todo esto? Es casi hora de que comience la clase."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1194
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_623dff54:

    # a angry blush "Y-You! See me at lunch and stay out of trouble, got it?" with dissolve
    a angry blush "¡T-tú! Te veo en el almuerzo y no te metas en problemas, ¿entendido?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1195
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_2670a5f9:

    # ks confused "Huh?"
    ks confused "¿Eh?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1196
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f1123740:

    # "Right. Nozomi's not what I should concern myself with right now."
    "Cierto. Nozomi no es lo que debería preocuparme en este momento."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1197
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_0bac3527:

    # ks "Oh, sure. See you at lunch."
    ks "Oh, claro. Te veo en el almuerzo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1199
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_348a2868:

    # "That was so fucking confusing. But at least she still wants to talk before taking whatever she thinks she has on me further up the chain." with dissolve
    "Toda esa mierda sí que fue confusa. Pero al menos aún quiere hablar antes de llevar sea cual sea el asunto que cree que tiene conmigo con autoridades más altas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1201
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f4e87fbc:

    # "Maybe there's hope for me yet..."
    "Tal vez aún tenga esperanza..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1205
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_3aeabe5f:

    # "Nozomi did eventually come into class, at practically the last second before Kobayashi took attendance. But I didn't dare look her way since then."
    "Nozomi sí llegó eventualmente a clase, prácticamente en el último segundo antes de que Kobayashi tomara asistencia, pero no me atreví a voltear a verla desde entonces."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1206
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_0afecea4:

    # "These other girls are out for blood right now, and I don't want to give them the ammunition."
    "Esas otras chicas tienen sed de sangre ahora mismo, y no quiero darles la munición."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1218
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_fef972ce:

    # "So I keep my head down, wait for the three of them to leave for what I assume is their daily rooftop meeting..."
    "Así que mantengo la cabeza baja, espero a que las tres se vayan a lo que asumo que es su reunión diaria en la azotea..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1220
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_c6257e7a:

    # "... Before I take my leave from the classroom and head to my own appointment with our student council president."
    "... Para posteriormente salir yo del salón e ir a mi propia reunión con la presidenta del consejo estudiantil."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1226
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f71a9b44:

    # a "Ah, there you are, Koyama. Please close the door behind you, then we'll get started."
    a "Ah, ahí estás, Koyama. Por favor, cierra la puerta al entrar, luego podemos comenzar."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1228
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_92543a29:

    # "My spine stiffens as I enter to find Akiko sat at a desk on the far side of the room."
    "Se me pone rígida la columna al entrar y encontrar a Akiko sentada en un escritorio al fondo de la habitación."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1230
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_2c3a24e2:

    # "I've never been in here before; never had to, but I know this place is usually a hive of activity this time of the year."
    "Nunca había estado aquí antes; nunca me hizo falta venir, pero sé que este lugar suele ser un enjambre de actividad en esta época del año."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1231
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_ea2292ea:

    # "Student council members are ran ragged trying to arrange all the miscellaneous busywork that goes into organising the annual school culture festival."
    "Los miembros del consejo estudiantil corren a toda prisa intentando concretar los distintos trabajos que requiere la organización del festival cultural escolar anual."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1232
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_7c361393:

    # a sleeptalk "S-so, um... Koyama..." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "P-pues, em... Koyama..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1233
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_bbfb0232:

    # ks confused "Yeah?"
    ks confused "¿Sí?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1234
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_9da561d4:

    # "But right now, it's just me and her. I thought they'd all be working through lunch, to be honest."
    "Pero ahora mismo, somos solo ella y yo. Pensé que estarían trabajando durante el almuerzo, siendo honesto."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1235
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_edabf38e:

    # a uniform armband smile "W-well first off, thanks for agreeing to talk again." with dissolve
    a uniform armband smile "B-bueno, primero que nada, gracias por acceder a volver a hablar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1236
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_cc1e4968:

    # "... I mean, it's not like you gave me a choice, is it?"
    "... Bueno, no es como si me hubieras dado opción, ¿o sí?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1237
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_9a360f70:

    # a sigh "A-and I'm really sorry about this morning. I think I made things even worse for you, but I didn't know how else to reach you at such short notice." with dissolve
    a sigh "Y-y de verdad lamento lo de esta mañana. Creo que te puse las cosas peor, pero no sabía de qué otro modo llegar a ti con tan poca antelación." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1238
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_70a13860:

    # a sad_side "Everything's so busy around here. You know, with the culture festival and everything. We can hardly catch a break." with dissolve
    a sad_side "Todo está muy ajetreado por aquí. Ya sabes, con el festival cultural y todo. Apenas podemos descansar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1239
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_7de0ae3f:

    # "She... really couldn't wait to talk to me again, huh?"
    "De... verdad no podía esperar para volver a hablar conmigo, ¿eh?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1240
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_e762dde2:

    # a sad "But I don't know, Kyou. Can I call you Kyou? It just feels to me like everyone's giving you a hard time for no good reason and... w-well, I can sympathize." with dissolve
    a sad "Pero no sé, Kyou. ¿Puedo llamarte Kyou? Me da la impresión de que todos te están jugando una mala pasada sin una buena razón y... b-bueno, puedo simpatizar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1241
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_3b49e28f:

    # "And now she sincerely believes I didn't do anything wrong the other day... huh."
    "Y ahora cree sinceramente que no hice nada malo el otro día... Vaya."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1242
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_ba703fb1:

    # a sleep "So with that in mind, I want you to know that you can come in here every lunchtime. At least for the next couple weeks before things get *really* hectic with the council." with dissolve
    a sleep "Así que, con eso en mente, quiero que sepas que puedes venir aquí cada almuerzo. Al menos el próximo par de semanas antes de que el consejo *en serio* sea un caos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1243
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_1d33452d:

    # a smile "It'll just be me here, we can lunch together and you can talk about anything you like." with dissolve
    a smile "Solo estaré yo aquí, podemos almorzar juntos y tú puedes hablar de lo que quieras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1244
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_b195f61a:

    # a uniform_down armband_down "So if you need any advice on your situation, or on talking to girls, or... well, anything that's on your mind, you can tell me in confidence." with dissolve
    a uniform_down armband_down "Por lo que, si necesitas algún consejo sobre tu situación, o cómo hablar con chicas, o... bueno, lo que sea que tengas en mente, dímelo con confianza." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1247
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_8e499c2f:

    # a happy "Maybe you'd just like to chat with someone in a safe environment? It's yours if you want it, Kyou." with dissolve
    a happy "¿Tal vez simplemente te gustaría charlar con alguien en un ambiente seguro? Es tuyo si lo quieres, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1248
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_0e6d20c3:

    # "I can feel the tension leaving my body as I come to stand by Akiko at her desk. To think I've been psyching myself up all night and morning for nothing."
    "Puedo sentir la tención abandonando mi cuerpo al pararme junto a Akiko en escritorio. Y pensar que me estuve mentalizando toda la noche y toda la mañana para nada. "

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1249
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_bfee53d9:

    # ks smile "Okay, sure. That sounds great, but can I ask you a weird question?"
    ks smile "Muy bien, claro. Eso suena genial, pero ¿puedo hacerte una pregunta rara?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1250
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_65d6945c:

    # a neutral "What's that?" with dissolve
    a neutral "¿Qué pregunta?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1251
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f76afe4b:

    # "And I'm sure this last test will confirm it beyond all doubt."
    "Y estoy seguro de que esta última prueba lo confirmaráa más allá de toda duda."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1252
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_adbd2c1a:

    # ks neutral "Have you ever been hypnotized before?"
    ks neutral "¿Alguna vez has sido hipnotizada?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1253
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_1360f192:

    # a drowsy "Hypnotized? I..." with dissolve
    a drowsy "¿Hipnotizada? Eh..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1254
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_c9527e0b:

    # "Akiko blinks slowly, seemingly a little confused by the question. But she quickly recovers to answer."
    "Akiko pestañea lentamente, al parecer un poco confundida por la pregunta. Pero pronto se recupera para contestar."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1255
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_be236182:

    # a neutral "No, I can't say I have been. Why do you ask?" with dissolve
    a neutral "No, no he tenido esa experiencia. ¿Por qué lo preguntas?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1256
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_8c24a0de:

    # "My improvised hypnosis on her was an unqualified success."
    "Mi sesión de hipnosis improvisada con ella fue un rotundo éxito."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1257
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_bb70b3a5:

    # ks smile "Oh, it was just a curiosity of mine, that's all."
    ks smile "Oh, solo curiosidad, es todo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1258
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_fd8ad6a3:

    # a smile "Heh. You know, this business with you and Nozomi made me look into hypnosis myself last night." with dissolve
    a smile "Je. Sabes, este asunto entre tú y Nozomi me hizo investigar un poco sobre hipnosis anoche." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1259
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_d77facb3:

    # "Her views on me completely changed, she went out of her way to meet me again, and she genuinely has no idea that I was behind it all."
    "Su visión de mí cambió por completo, buscó la manera de volver a verme, y no tiene ni remota idea de que yo estuve detrás de todo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1261
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_e9a68a79:

    # a happy "Psychology is a passion of mine, so it interests me a little bit." with dissolve
    a happy "La psicología es una de mis pasiones, así que me causa algo de interés." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1262
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_2e49c7f6:

    # "And now, thanks to her implanted need to see me again, she was compelled to get us more alone time, no matter how much it inconvenienced her."
    "Y ahora, gracias a su necesidad implantada de volver a verme, se vio impulsada a conseguirnos más tiempo a solas, sin importar lo inconveniente que fuera."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1264
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_39da21fe:

    # a neutral_side "I don't know if I'd ever use it in my line of work, but it wouldn't hurt to read up on it some." with dissolve
    a neutral_side "No sé si alguna vez la llegaré a usar en mi línea de trabajo, pero no me haría daño leer un poco al respecto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1265
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_4696f5e5:

    # "That I was able to do this to our student council president feels... well, it feels incredible."
    "Que haya sido capaz de hacerle esto a nuestra presidenta del consejo estudiantil se siente... bueno, se siente increíble."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1266
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_350db80d:

    # a smile "Ah, but you're kind of a hypnotist yourself now, aren't you? Do you have any thoughts on hypnotherapy?" with dissolve
    a smile "Ah, pero tú mismo eres algo así como un hipnotista ahora, ¿no? ¿Alguna opinión sobre la hipnoterpia?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1267
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_2a83355a:

    # "And I have to admit, it feels a lot easier to talk to her now I know what I can do to her."
    "Y he de admitir que se siente mucho más fácil hablar con ella ahora que sé lo que puedo hacerle."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1268
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_a129e297:

    # ks smirk "Kind of? What do you mean \"kind of\"?"
    ks smirk "¿Algo así? ¿Cómo que \"algo así\"?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1269
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_567b567f:

    # "But now I'm starting to think... if that's all true then Nozomi? She may not be genuinely into me after all."
    "Pero ahora que lo pienso... si todo eso es cierto, entonces, ¿Nozomi? Puede que realmente no esté interesada en mí después de todo."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1270
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f94dcb25:

    # a laugh "Ahaha, w-well I don't know if you could call yourself that yet. You hadn't done any practical hypnosis before Nozomi, right?" with dissolve
    a laugh "Ajaja, b-bueno, no sé si te puedas hacer llamar uno aún. No habías puesto la hipnosis en práctica antes de Nozomi, ¿verdad?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1271
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_904b2d73:

    # "After all, if my hypnosis, and my penlight, can do this kind of thing to the student council president, then it stands to reason that the same thing happened to her. "
    "Después de todo, si mi hipnosis y mi linterna pueden hacerle esto a la presidenta del consejo estudiantil, entonces es lógico que lo mismo le ocurrió a ella."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1272
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_247b3b3c:

    # ks neutral "I hadn't, but I'm well-read on the subject. And since my practical hypnosis on Nozomi was actually succeeding, I think it's fair to call myself a real hypnotist."
    ks neutral "No, pero he leído mucho sobre el tema. Y dado que mi hipnosis estaba siendo un éxito al ponerla en práctica con Nozomi, creo que es justo llamarme hipnotista."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1273
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_ae8ebe86:

    # a smile "That's fair enough, I suppose. You know way more than I do on the subject, that's for sure." with dissolve
    a smile "Tiene sentido, supongo. Sabes mucho más que yo sobre el tema, de eso estoy segura." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1274
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f0694100:

    # "She was only even considering a relationship with me because I made that suggestion to her."
    "Incluso estaba considerando una relación conmigo solo porque yo le hice esa sugestión."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1275
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_cfc74928:

    # "I don't know what her answer would've been had I asked her to speak truthfully, and without any suggestion she respond in the affirmative."
    "No sé cuál habría sido su respuesta si le hubiera pedido que hablara con sinceridad y sin ninguna sugestión."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1276
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_b7d2bdf8:

    # a neutral "All I know for sure is that it's not possible to hypnotize someone who is unwilling to be hypnotized." with dissolve
    a neutral "Lo único que sé con certeza es que no es posible hipnotizar a alguien que no quiera ser hipnotizado." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1278
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_006bdebd:

    # "And if I had simply told her she was in love with me, perhaps her true answer wouldn't have mattered?"
    "Y si sencillamente le hubiera dicho que estaba enamorada de mí, ¿quizás la verdadera respuesta no habría importado?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1279
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_2ad666bb:

    # a uniform armband laugh_wink "That's right, isn't it, Mr. Hypnotist?" with dissolve
    a uniform armband laugh_wink "Eso es correcto, ¿verdad, Sr. Hipnotista?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1280
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_5a552d93:

    # "I could try to change Nozomi. Just a little. Only enough that she'd see me the way I want her to see me. I'd just need another opportunity."
    "Podría intentar cambiar a Nozomi. Solo un poco. Solo lo suficiente para que me vea del modo que yo quiero que me vea. Solo necesitaría una oportunidad más."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1282
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_66367587:

    # "Assuming I could even get another opportunity. Unless..."
    "Asumiendo que siquiera pueda conseguir una oportunidad más. A no ser que..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1283
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_544c430a:

    # a smile "... Kyou?" with dissolve
    a smile "... ¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1284
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_8104650d:

    # "She might be able to help me. She's the student council president, after all. People listen to her; she could arrange a meeting."
    "Puede que ella sea capaz de ayudarme. Es la presidenta del consejo estudiantil, después de todo. La gente la escucha; podría organizarnos una reunión."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1286
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_88166004:

    # a sad "Hello? What's going on?" with dissolve
    a sad "¿Hola? ¿Qué sucede?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1287
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_38ac04a1:

    # "And despite that manipulative streak of hers, she seems to have a kind heart. She probably won't be very hard to convince."
    "Y a pesar de ese lado manipulador que tiene, parece ser de buen corazón. Probablemente no sea difícil de convencer."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1289
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_ed769271:

    # a neutral "Something the matter?" with dissolve
    a neutral "¿Ocurre algo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1290
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_9e23c525:

    # "It's surely something I could do, now that I have this penlight in my possession."
    "De seguro puedo hacerlo, ahora que tengo esta linterna en mi posesión."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1294
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_0939fb26:

    # a confused "Is there something in your eyes? You've got this stare going." with dissolve
    a confused "¿Tienes algo en los ojos? Tienes una mirada un tanto rara." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1294
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_7247a1cf:

    # "The possibilities right now seem almost endless..."
    "Las posibilidades ahora mismo parecen ilimitadas..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1295
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_b8b355ae:

    # a surprised "Oh come on, what are you doing? Say something!" with dissolve
    a surprised "Oh, por favor, ¿qué haces? ¡Di algo!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1296
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f51e2f8e:

    # "Oh, right. There's something I need to do first, before I can put any kind of plan into motion."
    "Oh, cierto. Hay algo que debo hacer primero, antes de poder poner cualquier plan en marcha."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1297
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_16e5c05f:

    # ks smile "... Hey, Akiko, what would you say to trying a little hypnosis right now?"
    ks smile "... Oye, Akiko, ¿qué te parecería probar un poquito de hipnosis ahora mismo?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1298
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_fa01c3a2:

    # a confused "Uh... I'm sorry, what?" with dissolve
    a confused "Eh... disculpa, ¿qué?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1299
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_00048c94:

    # "I'll need to entrance her again. My sudden question confuses her as I walk around her desk and stand behind her, while I gently place a hand on her shoulder."
    "Tendré que hipnotizarla otra vez. Mi pregunta repentina la confunde mientras rodeo su escritorio y me paro detrás de ella, poniendo gentilmente mi mano en su hombro."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1302
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_994f5f5d:

    # a "Now what are you doing? What's gotten into you?"
    a "Oye, ¿qué haces? ¿Qué mosco te picó?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1302
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_16e287f2:

    # ks neutral "Don't get up. I just want to demonstrate something, okay?"
    ks neutral "No te levantes. Solo quiero demostrar algo, ¿sí?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1305
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_49b5895c:

    # "A moment later I pull my penlight back from out of my pocket before switching it on and sweeping the light past her eyes as she looks up at me, startled." with dissolve
    "Un momento después, vuelvo a sacar la linterna de mi bolsillo, para después encenderla y pasar la luz por sus ojos mientras me mira alarmada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1308
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_f19d9a21:

    # a "Kyou, I don't..."
    a "Kyou, yo no..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1310
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_036ee49f:

    # ks "Shh, it's okay. You said it yourself, right?"
    ks "Shh, descuida. Tú misma lo dijiste, ¿verdad?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1315
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_c0cefa61:

    # ks "It's not possible to hypnotize someone who is unwilling to be hypnotized."
    ks "No es posible hipnotizar a alguien que no quiera ser hipnotizado."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1317
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_d6e96379:

    # ks "But if you're finding this light enticing to look at. If you're finding those patterns in your eyes driving your focus..."
    ks "Pero si mirar esta luz te parece tan encantador. Si los patrones que se forman ante tus ojos atrapan toda tu atención..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1319
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_a4f4675f:

    # ks "Driving you to relax, and stare, and sink..."
    ks "Haciendo que te relajes, y mires, y te hundas..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1322
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_02af1df7:

    # ks "Then it's perfectly, fine, perfectly natural to just sit here, and watch, and relax."
    ks "Entonces está perfectamente bien, es perfectamente natural sentarte, y observar, y relajarte."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1333
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_17556b61:

    # a uniform_down armband_down drowsy "Ahhh..."
    a uniform_down armband_down drowsy "Aaah..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1326
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_aea26a28:

    # ks "That's right. Perhaps you don't consciously remember these patterns that play across your eyes."
    ks "Eso es. Tal vez no recuerdes conscientemente estos patrones que pasan por tus ojos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1329
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_119b811e:

    # ks "But I bet your subconscious does."
    ks "Pero apuesto a que tu subconsciente sí los recuerda."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1330
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_99b66bd3:

    # a "{size=16}M-my...{/size}"
    a "{size=16}¿M-mi...{/size}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1333
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_0b9cd130:

    # a "{size=16}... subconscious?{/size}"
    a "{size=16}... subconsciente?{/size}"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1336
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_a67861c3:

    # ks "Don't worry about it. Just watch the light. And breathe. In..."
    ks "No te preocupes por eso. Solo observa la luz. Y respira. Inhala..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1339
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_2cfa3e65:

    # ks "And out. Feeling yourself become hypnotized. Just letting it happen. In..."
    ks "Y exhala. Siente cómo estás siendo hipnotizada. Solo deja que ocurra. Inhala..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1342
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_c2de6826:

    # ks "And out. Letting your eyelids become strained, becoming sleepy."
    ks "Y exhala. Deja que tus párpados se cansen, sintiendo más y más sueño."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1345
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_c5408e98:

    # ks "Closing those eyes and falling back into a hypnotic trance in three, two, one..."
    ks "Cierra tus ojos, y cae de regreso en un profundo trance en tres, dos, uno..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1365
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_3ce2ba0d:

    # ks "Sleep, Akiko. Dropping fast and deep now... that's right."
    ks "Duerme, Akiko. Cae rápida y profundamente... eso es."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1350
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_95784fc8:

    # "And once again, that's all it takes. Our student council president flops back in her chair, eyes closed with a peaceful expression."
    "Y una vez más, solo eso hace falta. Nuestra presidenta del consejo estudiantil se desploma en su silla con sus ojos cerrados y una pacífica expresión."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1351
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_d401448d:

    # ks "Dropping all the way down in that deep, familiar sensation of hypnosis."
    ks "Déjate llevar y caer en esa profunda y familiar sensación de hipnosis."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1369
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_a8b6981e:

    # "All I had to do was surprise her with this curious penlight of mine, talk calmly and it was no trouble at all to hypnotize her startled mind." with dissolve
    "Lo único que tuve que hacer fue sorprenderla con esta curiosa pluma linterna, hablar con calma, y no fue ningún problema hipnotizar su mente asustada." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1353
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_502db509:

    # ks "Ready to listen to my voice, hear only my voice. And accept any suggestion I make to you. Understand, Akiko?"
    ks "Lista para escuchar mi voz, oír nada más que mi voz. Y aceptar cada sugestión que te dé. ¿Entiendes, Akiko?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1354
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_ca1caf4e:

    # a sleeptalk "Yes... understand..." with dissolve
    a sleeptalk "Sí... entiendo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1355
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_836dc464:

    # "This penlight of mine really does do more than hypnosis, there's not a sliver of a doubt in my mind."
    "Esta linterna que tengo realmente hace más que hipnosis, no hay ni rastro de duda en mi mente."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1357
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_bb147bc4:

    # ks "That's wonderful, Akiko. It feels good to stay this deep and hypnotized. It feels good to listen to my voice, and accept my suggestions." with dissolve
    ks "Maravilloso, Akiko. Se siente bien estar hipnotizada tan profundamente. Se siente bien escuchar mi voz, y aceptar mis sugestiones." with dissolve

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1358
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_0d4c86aa:

    # "The possibilities of what I could do with her really do feel limitless. Is there truly no limit to how far I can bend and contort her mind into accepting my designs on her?"
    "Las posibilidades de lo que puedo hacer con ella realmente se sienten ilimitadas. ¿De verdad no hay límite en cuánto puedo doblar y torcer su mente a mi diseño?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1360
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_efc3bc74:

    # "Is it bad that I'm even thinking about this stuff? Or is it worse to waste this opportunity my own work has given me?"
    "¿Es malo que esté pensando en esto? ¿O es peor desperdiciar esta oportunidad que me ha dado mi propio trabajo?"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1361
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_993102bd:

    # "Yes. This is the opportunity I've been waiting for. This is how I take what's been denied me all these years."
    "Sí. Esta es la oportunidad que he estado esperando. Así es como tomaré lo que se me ha negado todos estos años."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1362
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_3a702cb0:

    # "This is how I'll make Nozomi mine."
    "Así es como volveré mía a Nozomi."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1363
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_aa127236:

    # "And our school council president is going to help me do it..."
    "Y nuestra presidenta del consejo estudiantil va a ayudarme a hacerlo..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1366
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_72a44bbc:

    # "((AUTHOR'S NOTE: Okay this is where we're at right now. I'll just explain the choices briefly and expand on one of them for the next update. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Muy bien, aquí es donde nos quedamos por ahora. Explicaré las decisiones brevemente y expandiré una de ellas en la próxima actualización. ))"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1367
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_097da290:

    # "In this path, Akiko becomes matchmaker, convinced Nozomi and Kyou are the perfect couple and is set on using her time and connections to bringing the two together."
    "En este sendero, Akiko se vuelve intermediaria, convencida de que Nozomi y Kyou son la pareja perfecta y se decide a usar su tiempo y conexiones para unirlos."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1368
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_7cec6624:

    # "So they spend the rest of lunch assembling some sort of plan that she'll enact that afternoon or the following day..."
    "Así que pasan el resto del almuerzo formando una clase de plan que ella pondrá en marcha esa tarde o al día siguiente..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1370
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_72a44bbc_1:

    # "((AUTHOR'S NOTE: Okay this is where we're at right now. I'll just explain the choices briefly and expand on one of them for the next update. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Muy bien, aquí es donde nos quedamos por ahora. Explicaré las decisiones brevemente y expandiré una de ellas en la próxima actualización. ))"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1371
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_b990f245:

    # "In this path, Kyou reasons that making Akiko his accomplice will only do so much, recalling how a hard a time she had with Nozomi's friends this morning."
    "En este sendero, Kyou concluye que volver a Akiko su cómplice no logrará mucho, recordando los problemas que tuvo con las amigas de Nozomi en la mañana."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1372
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_9747a3bc:

    # "But Akiko knows Nozomi, and he has this crazy thought, seeing her slumped in the chair as he imagines the love of his life sitting there..."
    "Pero Akiko conoce a Nozomi, y se le ocurre una loca idea, viéndola tumbada en la silla e imaginando al amor de su vida sentada ahí..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1373
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_ffeaf1bf:

    # "He asks her to recall everything she can about Nozomi: Her hair, her body language, her glasses, her manner of speaking..."
    "Le pide que recuerde todo lo que sabe de Nozomi: Su cabello, su lenguaje corporal, sus anteojos, su forma de hablar..."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1374
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_6b08ae08:

    # "How she's kind and loves to sing karaoke so beautifully (he assumes), and that she wants to be his girlfriend."
    "Cómo le gusta ir al karaoke y cantar de forma excelente (él asume), y que quiere ser su novia."

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1375
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_db5f19de:

    # "Because after all... she IS Nozomi!"
    "Porque, después de todo... ¡ella ES Nozomi!"

# game/kyou 3.rpy:1376
translate spanish Day3_Villain2_Kyou_9fb9c6d6:

    # "And that's all for now! Stay tuned for the next update~"
    "¡Y eso es todo por ahora! Manténganse en sintonía para la próxima actualización."

